\id MRK
\h Mak
\toc1 Toto Thovuye Utuniye Mak Le Rorori
\toc2 Mak
\toc3 Mak
\mt2 Toto Thovuye Utuniye
\mt1 Mak
\mt2 Le Rorori
\imt1 Utu iviva
\ip Mak, idae tembe th…®Ňčava Jon Mak, iye Banabas ighaiye (Kol 4:10) na utuutuniye ina Dagerawe Togha e t…®ne weiye Pol na Banabas th…® vakatha kaiwo vavana ekelesiya e t…®ne (Vak 12:25; 13:5 na 13; 15:36-39; 2Tim 4:11). Rarorori mevivako vavana th…®Ňčava Jon Mak vambe i wava Rom na ve yaku weiye Pita. (Tembe hu thuweva 1Pit 5:13) Na tembe th…®Ňčava Mak vambe i vavaghareŇčava Jisas le vakatha utuutuniye, va i loŇčwe weya Pita iyava i rori e bukuke iyake. Ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiye Mak va i roriya Jisas utuniye Rom ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwanji.
\ip Va e mbaŇčako iyako Rom lenji ghamba mbaro i lagh…®ye na thiye nuwanjiya i vur…®gheghe. Mak le bukuke e t…®ne i woraŇčgiya Jisas iye ravur…®gheghe: i vakathaŇčgiya vakatha ghamba rotaele th…® ghanagha, i vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® na i rakayathuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® e t…®ne.
\c 1
\s1 Jon Rabap…®taiso le vavaghare
\r (Mat 3:1-12; Luk 3:1-18; Jon 1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1-2 Utuutuke iyake Toto Thovuye Jisas Krais, Loi Nariye utuniye. I ri weya toto gharawo Ňčgoreiya Aiseya, Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va i rori Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya variya toto gharawo e ghamwan na i vivatha kamwath…® kaiwan.\x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Mal 3:1\x*
\v 3 Lolo regha i kulakula e njamnjam: ‚ÄėHu vivatha kamwath…® Giya kaiwae na hu varumwaru na mbala i reŇčawe.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:3 \xt Ais 40:3\x*
\p 
\v 4 Totoke gharawo iye Jon Rabap…®taiso. I yaku e njamnjam na i vavaghare weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi, amba Loi i numoten…®Ňčgi. Amba th…® bap…®taiso.
\v 5 Ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo Judiya na Jerusalem e t…®ne th…® rakarakamena weya Jon. Th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na i bap…®taisoŇčgi e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan. Na lenji bap…®taisoko i vatomwe kaero th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye Jon le vavaghare.
\v 6 Jon ghakwama th…® vakatha kamel vulivuliye. Mborowae gheva thetheghan njimwae. I ghan…®Ňčgiya bibita na Ňčguyo.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Jon ghakwama th…® vakatha kamel vulivuliye, ma njimwae, ma vulivuliye eŇčge. Jon ghakwamakova Ňčgoreiye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautuŇčgi. Jon ghakwama i vakatha ghar…®ghar…® th…® renuwaŇčakiki Ilaija. Ina Buk Boboma Teuye i govambwara (2KiŇč 1:8; Sak 13:4). Jiu va th…® renuwaŇča th…® munjeva Ilaija tembene i njoghamava mbaŇča regha na i vivathaŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Mesaiya le mena kaiwae (Mal 3:1; 4:5-6; hu thuwe Mak 9:12-13). Ghan…®Ňčga Jon va i ghan…®Ňčgi Ňčgoreiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® yaku e vur…®vur…® vwatavwata ghanji.\f*
\v 7 Le utu Ňčgorake: ‚ÄúLoloko iya i rereghamba e ghereiŇčguke iye i vur…®gheghe kivwalaŇčgo. Ghino, ma elo thovuye na val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya kururu na ya raka gheghe ghae.
\v 8 Ya bap…®taisoŇčga e mbwa ko iye ne i bap…®taisoŇčga e Nyao Boboma.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas ghabap…®taiso
\r (Mat 3:13-17; Luk 3:21-22)
\p 
\v 9 E mbaŇčako iyako e t…®ne Jisas i ri Nasaret Galili e t…®ne na i wa weya Jon, na iye i bap…®taiso Jor…®dan.
\v 10 MbaŇča Jisas i voro e mbwako ghadidiye i vaidiya buruburu i mavu na Nyao Boboma i njawe Ňčgoreiya bunebune.
\v 11 Amba ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i mena e buruburu iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen naruŇčgu moli gharegharethovuniye, i vakathaŇčgo ya warari lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas ghatanathetha
\r (Mat 4:1-11; Luk 4:12-13)
\p 
\v 12 E mbaŇčako iyako Nyao Boboma i vakatha na i wa e njamnjam vur…®vur…® vwatavwata.
\v 13 Na ve yaku gheko gheneyevar…®. Seitan i vatanathethaŇča. Va weiyaŇčgiya njamnjam thetheghan…®niye, ko Loi le nyao thovuthovuye th…® mena na th…® giya thalavuwe.
\s1 Jisas i woraweya le vavaghare r…®ghe Galili
\r (Mat 4:12-17; Luk 4:14-15)
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča vama th…® woruwo Jon e thiyo na e ghereiye,\f + \fr 1:14 \ft Hu thuwe Jon 6:17-18 na hu vaidi buda kaiwae Jon va ina e thiyo.\f* Jisas i wa Galili na i vavaghare Toto Thovuye i mena weya Loi,
\v 15 iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča kaero ina gheke, Loi le ghamba mbaro maiyavara; hu uturaŇčgiya lemi thar…®na na hu roiteteŇčgi na hu loŇčweghath…®gha Toto Thovuye.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i dage weŇčgiya raboroborogi theghevar…® na th…® ghambu
\r (Mat 4:18-22; Luk 5:1-11)
\p 
\v 16 Va mbaŇča regha Jisas i Ňčgalai Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye na i vaidiŇčgiya raboroborogi theghewo, Saimon na ghaghae Endru, th…® duda ghina kaiwae thiye raboroborogi.
\v 17 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu mena hu ghambuŇčgo na ya vavaghareŇčga ghemi ghar…®ghar…® ghanjirakosi.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 E mbaŇčako iyako th…® iteteŇčgiya lenji ghina na th…® ghambu.
\p 
\v 19 I loŇčga ghaova seiwo i vaidiya Jemes, Sebedi nariye, na ghaghae Jon. Thiye va inanji e lenji waŇčga th…® vavanamweŇčgiya lenji ghina.
\v 20 E mbaŇčako iyako i kula weŇčgi, th…® iteta ramanji Sebedi e waŇčga weiyaŇčgiya lenji rakakaiwo, na th…® ghambu.
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala weiye nyao raithar…®
\r (Luk 4:31-37)
\p 
\v 21 MbaŇča Jisas na gharaghambu th…® vutha Kapenaom, Sabat e t…®ne Jisas i ru Jiu e lenji Ňčgolo kururu na i vavagharewe.
\v 22 Ghar…®ghar…®ko iyava th…® vandeŇčeko gharenji i yo lagh…®ye le vavaghare kaiwae, kaiwae mava Ňčgoreiya mbaro gharavavaghare, ko i vavaghare weiye mbaro.
\p 
\v 23 E mbaŇčako iyako amala ina gheko nyao raithar…® inawe, va ina Jiu e lenji Ňčgolo kururuko t…®ne i yaro iŇča,
\v 24 ‚ÄúNe u vakatha vara budakai weime, Jisas rara Nasaret? Mo mena gheke na nuwaniya u vakowanaime? Kaero ya ghareghareŇčge, ghen Raboboma Loi va i variye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Jisas i Ňčael…®mbiya weya nyaoko raithar…® iŇča, ‚ÄúMeiye, na u iteteŇča amalana!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Nyaoko raithar…® i vandindi lagh…®ye amalako, i yaro lagh…®ye moli na i raŇčgiwe.
\v 27 Taulagh…®ko gharenji i yo lagh…®ye na th…® veutu weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBudakaiyake? Iyake vavaghare togha. Amalake i vavaghareŇča renuwaŇča emunjoru na totoghaŇčgi, na i vakatha weiye le mbaro, i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® na th…® loŇčweghath…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 28 Toto amalagh…®niye kaiwae i vagh…®liya Galili t…®neko lagh…®ye.
\s1 Jisas i thawariŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo
\r (Mat 8:14-17; Luk 4:38-41)
\p 
\v 29 MbaŇča Jisas na gharaghambu th…® roiteta Ňčgolo kururuko, weinjiyaŇčgiya Jemes na Jon, amba veth…® ru Saimon na Endru e lenji Ňčgolo.
\v 30 Saimon mboriyae i ghambwera, na mbe ina vara e ghambae riwae i dayagha na i ghena. Jisas vambe i vutha vara kaero th…® utugiyawe.
\v 31 I ruwe, i yalawe e n…®mae na i thalavu i thuweiru. Ghambwerama i iteteŇča na i vaŇčamweŇčgi.
\p 
\v 32 Varae vama ve ronja na kaero i mouwo na Sabat kaero iko, ghar…®ghar…® th…® bigimena weya Jisas ghambweghambwera na thavala nyao raithar…® ina weŇčgi.
\v 33 Ghar…®ghar…®ko taulagh…® e ghembako t…®ne th…® mevathavatha e Ňčgoloko mbothiye.
\v 34 Ghar…®ghar…® i ghanagha th…® ghambweraŇča ghambwera thaŇčar…® Jisas i thawarivaoŇčgi. Vambe i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiva nyao raraithar…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®. Mava i vatomwe na th…® dagewe kaiwae va th…® ghareghare thela amalagh…®niye, na iye i mena weya Loi.
\s1 Jisas ghamberegha i naŇčgonaŇčgo
\r (Luk 4:42-44)
\p 
\v 35 I liwiya ndayath…® Jisas i thuweiru, i iteta Ňčgolo na ghembako, i wa e val…®vaŇčga ma ghar…®ghar…® nanjiwe na ve naŇčgowe.
\p 
\v 36 Ko iyemaeŇčge e ghereiye Saimon na ghaune th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® tamwe.
\v 37 MbaŇča th…® vaidi, th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® tamwetamwe e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 38 Ko Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúRa raka e ghembaghemba vavanava e val…®vaŇčgake iyake na tembe va vavaghareweva. Iyake iyava kaiwae na ya mena.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 39 Iya kaiwae i vagh…®liya Galili lagh…®yeko, i vavaghareŇča Toto Thovuye e kururu ŇčgoloŇčgoloniyeko t…®nenji na i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…®.
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala i ghataŇča lepelo
\r (Mat 8:1-4; Luk 5:12-16)
\p 
\v 40 Amala regha i ghataŇča lepelo\f + \fr 1:40 \ft Lepelo gharumwaru ina Utu Gharumwaru e t…®ne Buk Boboma Toghake iyake ele ghambako t…®ne.\f*, va i mena weya Jisas i ronja e gheghe vuvuye e ghamwae na i naŇčgowe iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo nuwaniya, u vakathaŇčgo na ya thovuye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 41 Jisas ghare i v…®r…® kaiwae, i livamomoya n…®mae na i v…®ghath…®gha amalako. I dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaŇčguke nuwaiya, riwana i thovuye!‚ÄĚ
\v 42 E mbaŇčako iyako ghaghambwerama iko na riwae i th…®na.
\p 
\v 43 Amba i dage vur…®gheghewe na i variyeyathu e mbaŇčako iyako,
\v 44 na iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u vandeŇče, ne u ndeutuŇča weya lolo regha, u wawe vara ravowovowo na tembe ghan…®mberegha vo vatomweŇčgewe na vo vowo riwana le th…®na kaiwae Ňčgoreiya Mosese le mbaro, na i vaemunjoruŇča weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® riwan kaero i th…®na.‚ÄĚ
\v 45 Ko amalako i wa na ve utuutu weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® budakai me yomarawe. Iya kaiwae Jisas ma val…®kaiwae i ru e ghemba lagh…®ye ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo inanjiwe. I yaku eto e ghemba ma ghar…®ghar…®niye, ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® th…® menawe Galili lagh…®yeko e t…®ne.
\c 2
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala i kuvokuvo
\r (Mat 9:1-8; Luk 5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča amba gheviye eŇčge e ghereiye Jisas i njogha Kapenaom, ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweya toto kaero ina e Ňčgolo t…®ne.
\v 2 Woye lagh…®ye moli th…® mevathavatha. Th…® riyevanjara Ňčgolo t…®ne na ghae, amba i utuŇča Toto Thovuye weŇčgi.
\v 3 MbaŇčaniye gh…®mogh…®moru theghevar…® th…® wovutha amala i kuvokuvo ele ghamba ghena weya Jisas.
\v 4 Kaiwae wabwi i lagh…®ye moli, ma val…®kaiwanji th…® womena weya Jisas iya kaiwae th…® vakatha doda e Ňčgoloko vwatae i rukugh…®dagh…®da Jisas. MbaŇča vama th…® vakatha doda, th…® wonjaniya amalakowe, i ghena e da.
\v 5 Jisas i thuwe lenji loŇčweghath…®ko le lagh…®lagh…®ye, i dage weya kuvokuvoko iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, ya numotena len thar…®na wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ\fig Th…® vakwatenjoŇča amala regha i ghambwera e Ňčgolo vwatae|alt="Lowering the sick man to Jesus" src="lb00305c.tif" size="span" copy="BFBS (Bass)" ref="2:1-5"\fig*
\p 
\v 6 E mbaŇčako iyako mbaro gharavavaghare vavana thiya yaku gheko th…® rerenuwaŇča e gharenji th…®Ňča,
\v 7 ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae amalake i utu Ňčgoreiyako? Amalake i kivwala Loi na i utuvathar…®we! Ma te lolo reghava ne i numotena thar…®, Loi ghamberegha moli.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 E mbaŇčako iyako Jisas i ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga lenji renuwaŇča thuweleko, kaero i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae hu rerenuwaŇča Ňčgoreiyake?
\v 9 IyaŇčganiya ghautuutu i maya, ‚ÄėLen thar…®na kaero ya numoten,‚Äô o yaŇča, ‚ÄėU yondovir…®, u bigiya ghambana ghavwarara na u loŇčga‚Äô?
\v 10 Ya vaemunjoruŇča e ghemi, Lolo Nariye ele mbaro e yambaneke na val…®kaiwae i numotena thar…®.‚ÄĚ Amba i dage weya amalako kuvokuvoko iŇča,
\v 11 ‚ÄúYa dage e ghen, u yondo, u bigiya ghambana ghavwarara na u wa e len Ňčgolo!‚ÄĚ
\v 12 Taulagh…®ko e maranji i yondovir…®, i mbana ghambae ghavwarara na i loŇčgaraŇčgi. Gharenji i yo lagh…®ye moli na th…® taraweŇča Loi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa mbaŇča regha wo thuwathuwa Ňčgoraiyako va i vivako.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i kula weya Livai
\r (Mat 9:9-13; Luk 5:27-32)
\p 
\v 13 Jisas vambowo i njoghava Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye amba wabwi lagh…®ye th…® menawe na i vavaghare weŇčgi.
\v 14 I loŇčgaghao na i vaidiya Livai, Alipiyos nariye, i yaku e takis ghaopis, na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU ghambuŇčgo.‚ÄĚ Livai i yondovir…® na i ghambu.
\p 
\v 15 MbaŇča gheviye Jisas i ghan…®Ňčga Livai ele Ňčgolo. Takis gharamban…®mba na ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…® th…® mbela Jisas, th…® ghanagha th…® rakaru weŇčgi weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu e ghan…®Ňčgako.
\v 16 Mbaro gharavavaghare vavana, thiye Parisi, th…® thuwe Jisas i ghan…®Ňčga weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…® na takis gharamban, th…® dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae i ghan…®Ňčga weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…® na takis gharamban?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 MbaŇča Jisas i loŇčwevaidi amba iŇča, ‚ÄúThavala riwanji i thovuye ma nuwanjiya rathawathawari, ko mbe ghambweghambweraeŇčge nuwanjiya. Ma ya mena ya kula weŇčgiya thavala th…® rumwaru, ko ya mena thar…® gharavakatha kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Th…® vaito Jisas mbemba kaiwae
\r (Mat 9:14-17; Luk 5:33-39)
\p 
\v 18 Va mbaŇča regha Jon Rabap…®taiso gharaghambu na Parisi th…® mbeya ghan…®Ňčga Ňčgoreiye lenji kururu ghakamwath…®. Ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® mena weya Jisas na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae Jon gharaghambu na Parisi ghanjiraghambu th…® mbemba, ko ghen ghan…®raghambu nandere?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThare val…®kaiwae ghe gharaghaghayawo th…® mbeya ghan…®Ňčga mbaŇča ragheghe gh…®moru mbe inawe vara weiyaŇčgi? Ma val…®kaiwae! MbaŇča ragheghe gh…®moru mbe ina vara weiyaŇčgi mane th…® vakatha iyako.
\v 20 Ko mbaŇča ne i mena, nevole th…® vaŇčgu weŇčgiya ragheghe gh…®moru, mbaŇčako iyako amba th…® mbemba.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Mbowo i gotubweva iŇča, ‚ÄúMa lolo regha ne i liya kwama nasiye togha na i Ňčgiyagana kwama teuyewe i bowotu, kaiwae mbaŇča ne i thavwi na i livamo toghako ne i mwanavatha na i vakatha teuyeko na i mathethe na i bowoutu lagh…®ye.
\v 22 Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ma lolo regha i liŇčgiya waen togha e variye teuye th…® vakatha thetheghan njimwae, waen…®ko ne le vur…®gheghe kaiwae na i topo, waen i maliŇčgi na variyeko i thar…®. IyemaeŇčge waen togha i liŇčgi e variye togha.‚ÄĚ I dage Ňčgoreiye ma val…®kaiwae ra wovatabo vavaghare teuye weiye vavaghare togha.
\s1 Jisas na Parisi th…® wogaith…® Sabat kaiwae
\r (Mat 12:1-8; Luk 6:1-5)
\p 
\v 23 Va Sabat regha Jisas i ghathara wit e ghauma. Gharaghambu e lenji loŇčga t…®ne th…® lavugha wit uneune.
\v 24 Parisi th…® dage weya Jisas th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, buda kaiwae ghan…®raghambu mbaro i dageten e Sabat na th…® vakatha?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThare mbaŇča regha hu vaona Deivid va i vakatha budakai mbaŇča bada i ghar…®Ňčgi weiyaŇčgiya ghaune?
\v 26 Va i ru Loi ele Ňčgolo na i ghana bred boboma. Iyake va i yomara mbaŇča Abiyata iye va ravowovowo lagh…®ye. Mbaro vambe i vatomweŇčge ravowovowo weŇčgi th…® ghana bred…®ko iyako, ko Deivid va i ghan na tevambe i giya weŇčgiya ghaune.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae Loi i vakatha Sabat? Va i vakatha na i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®? Nandere moli! Ko iyemaeŇčge va i vakatha Sabat mbala val…®kaiwae th…® towowe e lenji kaiwo t…®ne.
\v 28 Iya kaiwae ghino Lolo Nariye ‚ÄĒ Ghino Sabat ghagiya. Elo mbaro na val…®kaiwae yaŇča ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakatha budakai Sabat e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\c 3
\s1 Amala n…®mae i mare na i kuvokuvo
\r (Mat 12:9-14; Luk 6:6-11)
\p 
\v 1 Amba Jisas tembe ve ruva Jiu e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne, na amala regha inawe n…®mae i kuvokuvo.
\v 2 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana va inanji gheko th…® njimbukiki na th…® thuwe thare ne i thawariya amalako e Sabat na mbala th…® wonjowe.
\v 3 Jisas i dage weya amalako iŇča, ‚ÄúU yondo na u mena u ndeghath…® gheke.‚ÄĚ
\v 4 Jisas i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBudakaiya la mbaro i vatomwe weinda na ra vakatha e Sabat? Ra vakatha thovuye o ra vakatha thar…®? Ra vamoru lolo yawaliye o ra vakowana?‚ÄĚ Ghar…®ghar…®ko thiya rokubaro.
\p 
\v 5 Jisas i gh…®maratako weŇčgi weiye le gaith…®, ko vambe ghare i v…®r…®va kaiwanji kaiwae gharenjiko i vur…®gheghe lagh…®ye, amba i dage weya amalako iŇča, ‚ÄúU livamomoya n…®man…®na.‚ÄĚ I livamomoya n…®maeko na kaero i thovuyeva.
\v 6 Parisi th…® raka iteta Jiu lenji Ňčgolo kururu na e mbaŇčako iyako th…® niva weinjiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® ghambugha Herod le mbaro, th…® tamwe kamwath…® na th…® un…®gha Jisas.
\s1 Wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rakambela Jisas
\p 
\v 7 Jisas na gharaghambu th…® raka e Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye na wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rakamena Galili th…® rakambele, vavana vambe th…® rakamenava Judiya,
\v 8 Jerusalem, Idumeya ele val…®vaŇčga na Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro na Taiya na Saidon mbe e lenji val…®vaŇčgava. Ghar…®ghar…® e ghembaghembake thiyake th…® raka menawe kaiwae va th…® loŇčweya le vakathako utuniye.
\v 9 Wabwiko va lagh…®ye moli iya kaiwae Jisas i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambuko th…® yambi ruwovamuna waŇčgako na i rovalawe mbala ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® romenawe moli.
\v 10 Vama i thawariŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo iya kaiwae thiye e ghanjighambwera nuwanjiya th…® rovur…®gheghe na th…® ghathara e wabwiko t…®ne th…® mena th…® v…®ghath…®.
\v 11 Na thembaŇča ghar…®ghar…® nyao raithar…® ina weŇčgi th…® thuwe, th…® dobu e ghamwae na th…® dage ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúOo! Ghen Loi Nariye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgi na ne th…® ndeutugiya weya lolo regha thela amalagh…®niye.
\s1 Jisas i tuthiŇčgiya ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® // theyaworo na theghewo
\r (Mat 10:1-4; Luk 6:12-16)
\p 
\v 13 MbaŇča Jisas i voro e ou nasiye i kula vathavathaŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru va nuwaiyaŇčgi. Th…® raka menawe,
\v 14 na i tuthiŇčgiya theyaworo na theghewo, na i uno idanji ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…®. Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMa tuthiŇčga na hu ghambuŇčgo. Ne ya variyeŇčga na vohu utuŇča ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu,
\v 15 na ne elo mbaro ghavur…®gheghe t…®ne na hu variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Theyaworo na theghewoke thiyake iya va i tuthiŇčgike: Saimon (Jisas va i rena Pita),
\v 17 Jemes Sebedi nariye na ghaghae Jon (va i uno idanji, Bowanje, gharumwaru Ňčgoreiye gharetaitai),
\v 18 Endru, Pilip, Batolomiu, Matiu, Tomas, Jemes Alipiyos nariye, Tadiyas, Saimon iye i mena e wabwi regha idanji Jilot,
\v 19 na Judas Isakariyot, iye Jisas ghaliliva.
\s1 Jisas na nyao raraithar…® ghanjigiya
\r (Mat 12:22-32; Luk 11:14-23; 12:10)
\p 
\v 20 Jisas i njogha na i ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne na wabwi lagh…®ye mbowo th…® mevathavathava, Jisas na gharaghambu mava e ghanjimbaŇča na val…®kaiwae th…® ghan…®Ňčga.
\v 21 MbaŇča le bodaboda th…® loŇčwe iyake, th…® wa na veth…® yalaweghath…® kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúUmbaliye i ghawe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Mbaro gharavavaghare vavana th…® mena Jerusalem th…® utuŇča th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNyao raraithar…® ghanjigiya Bil…®sabul inawe! Nyao raraithar…® lenji randeviva iya i giya vur…®gheghekowe na i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyaoko raraithar…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Lenji utuko kaiwae, Jisas i kula vathaŇčgi na th…® raka menawe amba i goghaimba na i veŇčgi iŇča: ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga ne Seitan iŇča na i variyeraŇčgiya ghamberegha?
\v 24 ThoŇčgo ghamba mbaro regha tembe ghamberegha i yondo na i giya wabwi na th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi, ghamba mbaroko iyako ne i dobu.
\v 25 Na thoŇčgo Ňčgolo regha ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® rakayondo na th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi, Ňčgolo iyako ghar…®ghar…®niye ne nandereŇčgi.
\v 26 Na thoŇčgo Seitan i vakatha wabwi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne na th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi, mane te i vur…®ghegheva, ne i dobu na kaero iko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 ‚ÄúMa lolo regha val…®kaiwae i ru amala vur…®gheghe ele Ňčgolo na i kaiva le bigibigi e Ňčgoloko t…®ne. ThoŇčgo nuwaiya wo i yalawekai, i Ňčgar…®ghath…® e thiyo, ko amba i kaiva le bigibigi e Ňčgoloko t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® na lenji utuvathar…® weya Loi, Loi i numoten…®Ňčgi.
\v 29 Ko thela i utuvathar…® weya Nyao Boboma, Loi ma tene i numoten…®va loloko iyako; kaiwae i vakatha thar…® iya Loi ma mbaŇča regha tene i numoten…®va.‚ÄĚ
\v 30 Jisas iŇča Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® va th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNyao raithar…® inawe.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas t…®nae na oghaghaeŇčgi moli
\r (Mat 12:46-50; Luk 8:19-21)
\p 
\v 31 Amba Jisas t…®nae na oghaghae th…® vutha. Th…® ndeghath…® eto na th…® variya utu kaiwae nuwanjiya i raŇčgi na th…® utu weinji.
\v 32 Wabwi lagh…®ye va th…® rogh…®liŇča, th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúT…®na na oghagha thiye etoke th…® vavaito kaiwan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNava thela na oghaghaŇčguŇčgiya thavala?‚ÄĚ
\v 34 I thuweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iya va th…® rogh…®liŇčako, na iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! Thiyake nava na oghaghaŇčgu!
\v 35 Thela thoŇčgo i vakatha Loi le renuwaŇča iye ghaghaŇčgu, louŇčgu na t…®naŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\c 4
\s1 I goghaimba rayathu weiwo kaiwae
\r (Mat 13:1-9; Luk 8:4-8)
\p 
\v 1 Jisas vambowo i vavaghareva e Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye. Wabwiko iyava th…® megh…®liŇčako i lagh…®ye moli iya kaiwae va i tha e waŇčga na i rovalawe. I ghagharaŇčgi seiwo na wabwiko lagh…®ye thiya yaku e malavwata.
\v 2 Va i vavaghareŇčgiya bigibigi i ghanagha. Vambe i goghaimba eŇčge. I dage weŇčgi iŇča,
\v 3 ‚ÄúHu vandeŇče! Amala regha i wa na ve yathu le weiwo.
\v 4 MbaŇča i yathu le weiwoko e umako vavana th…® dobu e kamwath…® mara na ma th…® mena th…® ghan…®Ňčgi.
\v 5 Vavana th…® unja e thelau ele var…®var…® na mava thelauko i poku, na Ňčgorava th…®Ňčama kaero th…® yovoro kaiwae thelauko mava i poku.
\v 6 MbaŇča varae i Ňčge thelauko na i dayagha kaero th…® mare kaiwae wathelilinji ma vamba ina bwagabwaga.
\v 7 Weiwo vavana i yathu Ňčgora nana raraithar…® inanjiwe. Nanako raraithar…® lenji mbuthu i maya na th…® vwariŇčgi na ma th…® rau.
\v 8 Ko weiwo vavana va th…® unja e thelau thovuye, th…® mbuthu wagiyawe na th…® rau na uneunenji lenji ghanaghanagha i tomethi, vavana vogh…®yeto (30), vavana vogh…®yewona (60) na vavana vogh…®thaŇčar…® (100).‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo e yanayanawami hu vandeŇče wagiyaweya ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Buda kaiwae Jisas i goghaimba
\r (Mat 13:34-35; Luk 8:9-10)
\p 
\v 10 MbaŇča Jisas vambe ghamberegha eŇčge, ghar…®ghar…®ko iyava th…® vandeŇčeko vavana th…® menawe weinjiyaŇčgiya gharaghambuko theyaworo na theghewoko. Th…® dagewe na i vamanjamanjalaŇča goghaimbako weŇčgi. Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča,
\v 11 ‚ÄúE ghemi Loi le ghamba mbaro gharenuwaŇča thuwele kaero i woraŇčgiya weŇčga. Ko thavala ma inanji Loi ele wabwi Loi le ghamba mbaro emunjoru utuutuniye th…® loŇčwe e goghaimba.
\v 12 Kaiwae Buk Teuye iŇča, ‚ÄėOthembe ne th…® njimbukiki mane th…® thuwe; ne th…® vandeŇče mane th…® ghareghare. Kaiwae thoŇčgo th…® thuwe na th…® ghareghare th…® roiteteŇčgiya lenji thar…®, th…® goru weya Loi, na ne i numoten…®Ňčgiya lenji thar…®.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Ais 6:9-10\x*
\s1 Goghaimba rayathu weiwo gharumwaru
\p 
\v 13 Amba Jisas i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMa hu ghareghare goghaimbake iyake? ŇägoroŇčga ne huŇča eŇčge na hu ghareghareŇčgiya goghaimbako wolagh…®ye?‚ÄĚ
\v 14 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúWo ya vamanjamanjalaŇča weŇčga, rakabu weiwo Ňčgora i kabu Loi ghal…®Ňčae.
\v 15 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana Ňčgoranjiya weiwo th…® dobu e kamwath…® mara; e mbaŇčako iyako th…® loŇčweya Loi ghal…®Ňčae, Seitan i mena na i woraŇčgiya weŇčgi.
\v 16 Vavana Ňčgoranjiya weiwo th…® dobu e thelau ele var…®var…®. E mbaŇčako iyako th…® loŇčweya Toto Thovuye, th…® wovatha weinji lenji warari.
\v 17 Ko ma i ru moli e gharenji Ňčgora nana ma e wathewatheliliye thovuye na ma th…® yaku mbaŇča molao. MbaŇča vuyowo ne i vutha weŇčgi o ghar…®ghar…® th…® botewoŇčgi Toto Thovuye kaiwae, e mbaŇčako iyako th…® dobu.
\v 18 Vavana ŇčgoranjiŇčgiya weiwo th…® dobu Ňčgora nana raraithar…® inanjiwe. Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake th…® loŇčweya Loi ghal…®Ňčae,
\v 19 ko yambaneke renuwaŇčaniye i vagaghala nuwanji na nuwanjiko i ghaŇčgo weya gogomwau na nuwanjiya lemoyo, iyake kaiwae ma te th…® goruweva Loi ghal…®Ňčae. Thiye ŇčgoranjiŇčgiya weiwo ma e uneune.
\v 20 Ko ghar…®ghar…® vavana Ňčgoranjiya weiwo th…® dobu e thelau thovuye. Th…® loŇčweya Loi ghal…®Ňčae, th…® loŇčweghath…® na th…® worawe e gharenji na i rau; vavana vogh…®yeto (30), vavana vogh…®yewona (60) na vavana vogh…®thaŇčar…® (100).‚ÄĚ
\s1 Kad…®ŇčeŇče i giya manjamanjala
\r (Luk 8:16-18)
\p 
\v 21 Jisas i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThare mbaŇča regha lolo regha i th…®n…®ruwo kad…®ŇčeŇče na i th…®n…®rawe e uye t…®ne o e tebol ghamba ghena raberabe? Ma i th…®n…®vakwate?
\v 22 Budakaiya i rothuwele tene Loi i woraŇčgiya e manjamanjala, na budakaiya e ghayaboyabo tene i tatethewo.
\v 23 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami, hu vandeŇče wagiyawe ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke na hu ghareghare!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúHu vakaiwoŇča yanayanawamina na hu vandeŇče wagiyawe; kaiwae thoŇčgo hu vandeŇče na hu ghambu, amba ne val…®kaiwami hu ghareghare wagiyawe. Thela i ghareghare othembe mbema seiwo eŇčge, weya amalagh…®niye Loi ne i woraŇčgiyawe lagh…®ye. Ko the lolo ma ele ghareghare othembe the utu i loŇčwe ne i ghawewe.
\v 25 Iyake Ňčgoreiye, thoŇčgo u wo ne i giya e ghen ma e vwataeva, ko thoŇčgo ma u wo mun, ne u th…®vaivao iyana othembe budakai ina e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Weiwo tembe ghamberegha i mbuthu ghagoghaimba
\p 
\v 26 Jisas vambowo i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgoreiya amala regha i raŇčgi na ve yathu weiwo ele uma t…®ne.
\v 27 I njogha gougou na i ghena ghararagh…®ye i kaiwo mbaŇča regha na regha, weiwoko i yovoro na i mbuthu, ko ma i ghareghare eŇčge ŇčgoroŇčga le mbuthumbuthu.
\v 28 Weiwoko tembe ghamberegha i mbuthu e thelauko na i rau: i viva mborowae, vunyenyeuye amba muyai uneune th…® rakaraŇčgi.
\v 29 MbaŇča uneune th…® mweghe i wo le kaina na ve ten…®we kaiwae kaero ghambaŇča.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mas…®ted weiwae ghagoghaimba
\r (Mat 13:31-32,34; Luk 13:18-19)
\p 
\v 30 Jisas mbowo i dage weŇčgiva iŇča, ‚ÄúMbowo ya utugiyava utuutu regha e ghemi, na i manjamanjala e ghemi ŇčgoroŇčga Loi le ghamba mbaro ghayamoyamo.
\v 31 Ňägoreiya mas…®ted mbouye\f + \fr 4:31 \ft Mas…®tedke iyake ghar…®ghar…® th…® kabu e lenji uma na th…® vakaiwoŇča kaiwae i giya ghaniŇčga gham…®nae thovuye, Ňčgoreiye th…® vakaiwoŇča njigh…®. Iyake ma ndiya th…® ghawi weiye gh…®leth…®.\f* le mbuthumbuthu. Weiwoke wolagh…®ye th…® kabukabu e uma nasiyeninji moli.
\v 32 MbaŇča th…® wokabu na i mbuthu, i mbuthu kivwalaŇčgiya ghan…®Ňčgako wolagh…®ye e umako t…®ne. YaŇčgayaŇčgae lagh…®lagh…®ye na ma th…® yoyo val…®kaiwae th…® vakatha unyinji e riburibuwae.‚ÄĚ
\v 33 Jisas va i vavaghareŇčaŇčgiya goghaimba i ghanagha Ňčgoranjiya iyake weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, na val…®kaiwae nuwanjiko i manjamanjalawe.
\v 34 Vambe i goghaimba eŇčge iyava i utu weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko, ko mbaŇča vambe thiye eŇčge weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambuko i vamanjamanjalaŇča bigibigiko wolagh…®ye weŇčgi.
\s1 Jisas i dagewe ndewendewe na i mare
\r (Mat 8:23-27; Luk 8:22-25)
\p 
\v 35 Va yegh…®yegh…®ye e mbaŇčako iyako i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu iŇča, ‚ÄúRa lawaoko val…®mbwako.‚ÄĚ
\v 36 Th…® iteteŇčgi wabwi lagh…®ye, th…® tha e waŇčgako Jisas vama inakowe na weinji. WaŇčga vavana vambe weinjiyaŇčgiva.
\v 37 Amba ndewendewe lagh…®ye i rowo, bagodu i vana e waŇčga na i nja e waŇčgate na mbalavama th…® dama.
\v 38 Jisas ina e waŇčgako t…®ne i ghena e waŇčgako ghar…®ghe na i wara umbaliye e bubuthe. Gharaghambu th…® yavair…® na th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, thare u rerenuwaŇča kaiwanda, mbaŇča nasiye raya mare!‚ÄĚ
\v 39 Jisas i thuweiru na i dage weŇčgiya ndewendewe na bagoduko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu towo! Hu ndeghath…®!‚ÄĚ MbaŇčara ndewendewe na bagodu th…® towo na tad lagh…®ye i ghagha.
\v 40 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae hu mararu? Ma e lemi loŇčweghath…®?‚ÄĚ
\v 41 Th…® mararu lagh…®ye moli na th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThelake? Othembe ndewendewe na bagodu th…® loŇčweghath…® ghal…®Ňčae.‚ÄĚ
\c 5
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala nyao raraithar…® nanjiwe
\r (Mat 8:28-34; Luk 8:26-39)
\p 
\v 1 Jisas na gharaghambu va veth…® vuthava Galili Njigh…®niye ele val…®vaŇčga regha iya Gerasa ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® yakukowe.
\v 2 MbaŇča i iteta waŇčga amala regha i rukuraŇčgimawe e ghabughabubuko. Amalake nyao raithar…® inawe
\v 3 na i yaku e ghabubuko. I vur…®gheghe lagh…®ye moli na ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha i Ňčgar…®ghath…® othembe th…® Ňčgar…® e sen.
\v 4 MbaŇča i ghanagha ghar…®ghar…® th…® Ňčgara n…®man…®ma na gheghe e sen, ko mbaŇča regha na regha th…® vakatha i bebeŇčgiya sen…®Ňčgiko e n…®man…®mako na i bebevowowona sen…®Ňčgiko e ghegheko. Ma lolo regha val…®kaiwae i laweghath…® na i mbaroŇča.
\v 5 Ghararagh…®ye na gougou i loŇčgatakweŇčgiya ghabughabubu na e bobokulu vwatavwatanji, i yaroyaro na i tena riwariwae e var…®var…®.
\p 
\v 6 Vamba ina bwagabwaga kaero i vaidiya Jisas; i ruku na i mena i kururu e ghamwae.
\v 7-8 MbaŇčako iyako Jisas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNyao raithar…®, u raŇčgi weya amalana!‚ÄĚ Nyaoko raithar…® i yaro ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúJisas, Loi Ramevoro Moli Nariye! Nuwaniya budakai ina e ghino? Loi e idae ya naŇčgo e ghen ne u ndevakatha v…®r…® lagh…®ye e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Jisas i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúIdan thela?‚ÄĚ Amalako i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúIdaŇčgu woye lagh…®ye moli\f + \fr 5:9 \ft ‚ÄúIdaŇčgu woye lagh…®ye moli‚ÄĚ Idake iyake vaŇča Grik ‚ÄúLijon‚ÄĚ, gharumwaru Ňčgoreiyake: Rom lenji ragagaith…® wabwi regha, lenji ghanaghanagha paeb tausan (5,000).\f* ‚ÄĒ kaiwae lamamoyo moli.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 I naŇčgo vur…®gheghe weya Jisas na thava i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgi e val…®vaŇčgako iyako t…®ne.
\p 
\v 11 Mbombo naura inanji thiya nuve e bobokulu regha ghadidiye.
\v 12 Nyaoko raraithar…® mbowo th…® naŇčgoweva th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU variyeime weŇčgiya mbomboko na vo ru weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 13 Iya kaiwae Jisas i vatomweŇčgi i variyeŇčgiya nyaoko raraithar…® th…® rakaraŇčgi weya amalako na th…® rakaru weŇčgiya mbomboko. Mbomboko naura lenji ghanaghanagha mbalavama i wo tu tausan th…® rakanjaniya bobokuluko ghadidiye na vethiya munja e njigh…®.\fig Nyao raraithar…® th…® naŇčgo weya Jisas na th…® rakaru weŇčgiya mbomboko|alt="spirits into the pigs" src="Lk8.26.tif" size="span" copy="UBS (GNR)" ref="5:13"\fig*
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča mbomboko gharanjimbunjimbu th…® thuwe iyako, th…® rakavo na veth…® ututako ghembako lagh…®ye na e umauma t…®net…®nenji. Iya kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo th…® raka na veth…® thuwe budakai me yomara.
\v 15 MbaŇča th…® rakamena weya Jisas, th…® vaidiya amalako nyaoma raraithar…® menanjiwe. I yaku gheko, i njimbo ri na umbaliye kaero i thovuye; na taulagh…®ko thiya mararu lagh…®ye.
\v 16 Thavala inanjiwe th…® utugiya ghar…®ghar…®ko weŇčgi ŇčgoroŇčga nyaoko raraithar…® meth…® rakaraŇčgi weya amalako na budakai me ghar…®Ňčgiya mbomboma.
\v 17 MbaŇča th…® loŇčwevaidi th…® naŇčgo vur…®gheghe weya Jisas na i iteteŇča lenji val…®vaŇčgako.
\p 
\v 18 MbaŇča Jisas vama i tha vara e waŇčgako amba amalako nyaoma raraithar…® menanjiwe i naŇčgo vur…®gheghewe na i wa weiye.
\p 
\v 19 Ko Jisas mava i vatomwe. IyemaeŇčge i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU njogha e ghamban weŇčgiya len bodaboda na voutu weŇčgi ŇčgoroŇčga Giya le vakatha na le gharev…®r…® le lagh…®lagh…®ye e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 Amalako i iteteŇčgi na i ruvao e ghembaghembama ghembayaworoma, i utuŇča bigibigiko lagh…®lagh…®ye budakai Jisas me vakathakowe. Taulagh…®ko th…® loŇčwe na gharenji i yo lagh…®ye.
\s1 Jairas i naŇčgo weya Jisas i thalavu yawarumbuye
\r (Mat 9:18-26; Luk 8:40-56)
\p 
\v 21 Jisas na gharaghambu th…® njogha Galili Njigh…®niye val…®vaŇčga. Woye lagh…®ye th…® megh…®liŇča.
\v 22 Amala regha idae Jairas, iye Ňčgolo kururu gharambarombaro regha, i vutha. MbaŇča i thuwe Jisas i dobu e gheghe,
\v 23 na i naŇčgo weiye ghare le vatomwe weya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúYawarumbuŇčgu nasiye i ghambwera lagh…®ye moli. NuwaŇčguiya weiŇčgu ghen vo bigiraweya n…®man…®man…®na e vwatae na riwae i thovuye, thava i mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Amba Jisas i wa weiye. Ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo moli weinji, vavana e njawanjawaeŇčgi, vavana e ghamwae na vavana e ghereiye.
\s1 Jisas i thawariya ela eunda
\p 
\v 25 Ela eunda i ghataŇča voruvoru theghathegha hoyaworo na umboiwo e t…®ne.
\p 
\v 26 Rathawathawari i ghanagha va th…® mando na th…® thawari. I th…®vaivao le bigibigi weŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge ma riwae i thovuye, vama i vur…®gheghe eŇčge.
\v 27 Vama i loŇčweya Jisas le vakatha utuutuniye, iya kaiwae i ghathara wabwiko e t…®nenji Jisas e ghereiye,
\v 28 na tembe i dageweva ghamberegha iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ma ya v…®ghath…® eŇčge ghakwamako, wo ghambwerake ne iko.‚ÄĚ
\v 29 I v…®ghath…®gha ghakwamako na e mbaŇčako iyako voruvoruko iko na i gham…®no riwaeko e t…®ne ghaghambwerako kaero iko.
\v 30 E mbaŇčako iyako Jisas i gham…®no vur…®gheghe vama i raŇčgiwe, iya kaiwae i matav…® weŇčgiya wabwiko na i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThela me v…®ghath…®gha wo kwamake?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Gharaghambuko th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe wabwi lagh…®ye moli th…® ndegh…®liŇčaŇčge, na buda kaiwae uŇča, ‚ÄėThela me v…®ghath…®Ňčgo?‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Ko Jisas i gh…®maratakwa ghadidiye, nuwaiya i vaidiya thela me v…®ghath…®.
\v 33 Elako vama i ghareghare budakai me yomarawe, i mena weya Jisas weiye le mararu na le gharelagh…®lagh…®, i ronja e gheghe vuvuye Jisas e gheghe na i utugiyawe utuutuniyeko wolagh…®ye.
\p 
\v 34 Jisas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúYawarumbuŇčgu, len loŇčweghath…® kaero i vamoruŇčge. U wa wein len gharemal…®l…®. Ghan…®v…®r…® kaero iko.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i thawariya Jairas yawarumbuye
\p 
\v 35 Jisas vamba i utuutu weya elako ghar…®ghar…® vavana kaero th…® vutha, th…® mena Jairas ele Ňčgolo na th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúYawarumbuma kaero me mare. Buda kaiwae u rombelembela Ravavagharena?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 36 MbaŇča i loŇčwevaidi lenji utuko, mava i goruwe, ko i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúTha u mararu, ma u loŇčweghath…® eŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\v 37 MbaŇča th…® wareri, ma tembe i vatomweva lolo regha na weiye, vambe Pita eŇčge Jemes na ghaghae Jon.
\v 38 MbaŇča th…® vutha Jairas ele Ňčgolo Jisas i vaidiya numounouno na i loŇčweya thiya randa na th…® raŇčivetho lagh…®ye moli.
\v 39 I ru na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda ghanumounounoke? Buda kaiwae huya randa? Ňägamake ma i mare, mbema i ghena eŇčge!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 40 Taulagh…®ko th…® vav…®ra Jisas. I dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgi na th…® rakaraŇčgi e Ňčgoloko, amba i vaŇčguŇčgiya Ňčgamako ramae na t…®nae na gharaghambu theghetoko, na th…® ru Ňčgorava Ňčgamako inawe.
\v 41 I v…®ghath…® e n…®mae na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúTalitha kum,‚ÄĚ gharumwaru, ‚ÄúWevo nasiye, ya dage e ghen, u thuweiru!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 42 E mbaŇčako iyako wevoko i thuweiru na i loŇčga (ghatheghathegha va hoyaworo na umboiwo), na e mbaŇčaniye gharenji i yo lagh…®ye moli.
\v 43 Ko Jisas i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgi thava th…® utugiya weya lolo regha budakaiya me vakathawe. Amba iŇča, ‚ÄúHu giya ghan…®Ňčgawe!‚ÄĚ
\c 6
\s1 Nasaret ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® botewo Jisas
\r (Mat 13:53-58; Luk 4:16-30)
\p 
\v 1 Jisas va i iteta ghembako iyako na i njogha weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu e ghambae moli.
\v 2 Sabat e t…®ne i vavaghare Jiu e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne. Ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo va inanji gheko na mbaŇča th…® loŇčweya le vavaghareko gharenji i yo lagh…®ye na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalake iyake, aŇčga mendava ve wo ghareghareke thiyake? Thambo thimbake na aŇčga mendava ve wo na i vakathaŇčgiya vakathake ghamba rotaele thiyake?
\v 3 Mbema kapentama iyana, Meri nariye na oghaghae Jemes, Josep, Judas na Saimon. Oloulouye mbe inanji gheke.‚ÄĚ Gharenji i gaith…®wana na th…® botewoyathu.
\p 
\v 4 Iya kaiwae Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…® e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye th…® yavwatatawana Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, ko ghambae ghar…®ghar…®niye, gheuu ghar…®ghar…®niye na le bodaboda mava th…® yavwatatawana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Kaiwae ma th…® loŇčweghath…®, ma val…®kaiwae i vakatha mun vakatha ghamba rotaele regha gheko ko vambe i lirawe eŇčge n…®mae ghambweghambwera vavana e riwanji na riwanji i thovuye.
\v 6 Ghare i yo lagh…®ye kaiwae mava e lenji loŇčweghath…®.
\p Amba Jisas i wa e ghembaghemba e val…®vaŇčgako iyako na i vavaghare weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.
\s1 Jisas i variyeŇčgiya ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® // theyaworo na theghewo
\r (Mat 10:5-15; Luk 9:1-6)
\p 
\v 7 Jisas i kula vathavathaŇčgiya gharaghambu theyaworo na theghewo na i variyeŇčgi, theghewo iya. I giya mbaro weŇčgi na val…®kaiwae th…® variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.
\v 8 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúE lemi loŇčgana t…®ne, ne hu ndewo bigi reghava, ghan…®Ňčga o raloŇčgaloŇčga lenji nambo o mani, mbe pwasike eŇčge.
\v 9 Hu njimbo gheghemi ghae, ko ne hu ndeliya kwama yaŇčgarava.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Tembe i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča vohu vutha e ghemba na th…® kula vathaŇčga, hu yaku e Ňčgoloko iyako ghaghad hu itete ghembako iyako.
\v 11 ThoŇčgo hu vutha e ghemba na ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® kula vathaŇčga o ma th…® loŇčweya lemi utu, hu iteta ghembana iyana. MbaŇča hu iteteŇča hu tagavughethu vughana e gheghemina. Iyake ne i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčgi Loi i botewoyathuŇčgi kaiwae ma th…® loŇčweya lemi utuna.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® vavaghare mbala ghar…®ghar…® th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi.
\v 13 Th…® variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® na th…® liŇčgiya bunama idae oliv…® ghambweghambwera e riwanji na riwanji i thovuye.
\s1 Jon Rabap…®taiso le mare
\r (Mat 14:1-12; Luk 9:7-9)
\p 
\v 14 KiŇč Herod i loŇčweya Jisas le kaiwo utuutuniye, kaiwae utuniye vama i vagh…®liya Galili lagh…®yeko. Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas utuniye ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúJon Rabap…®taiso kaero mendava i thuweiru na ma e yawayawaliyeva. Iya kaiwae vur…®gheghe inawe na i vakathaŇčgiya vakathake ghamba rotaele thiyake.‚ÄĚ
\v 15 Vavana th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúIye Ilaija.‚ÄĚ Na vavana mbe th…®Ňčava, ‚ÄúIye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Ňčgoreiya va Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu i vivako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča Herod i loŇčweya Jisas utuniye kaero iŇča, ‚ÄúJon Rabap…®taiso iyako! Va yaŇča na th…® kitena numwema, ko mendava i thuweiru na kaero e yawayawaliyeva.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Herod i loŇčweghath…® iyake kaiwae va mbaŇča regha i variyeŇčgiya ragagaith…® na th…® yalaweya Jon, th…® Ňčgar…® na th…® woruwo e thiyo. Herod va i vakatha Ňčgoreiyako Herodiyas kaiwae, kaiwae vama i vaŇčgu othembe elagh…®niye ghaghae Pilip levo.
\v 18 Jon iye va i vathivalaŇča weya Herod iŇča, ‚ÄúMa mbaro i vatomwe na u vaŇčgwa ghaghan…®na levo!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Iya kaiwae Herodiyas ghare i gaith…®wana Jon na nuwaiya i un…®gh…®, ko mava val…®kaiwae,
\v 20 kaiwae Herod va i mararu Jon na i ghareghare iye lolo rumwarumwaruniye na i boboma; vambema i njimbukikiya eŇčge. MbaŇča regha na regha Herod mbe i loŇčwa Jon othembe ghare mava i warariŇča na ma i ghareghare mbala ne i vakatha.
\p 
\v 21 MbaŇča regha amba Herodiyas ghambaŇča thovuye regha i mena na i un…®gha Jon. E mbaŇčako iyako Herod i vakatha le ghamb…® gharenuwaŇčakiki ghathaga, amalagh…®niye lenji rakakaiwo lagh…®lagh…®ye, ragagaith…® lenji randevivaŇčgi na Galili giyagiyaniye kaiwanji.
\p 
\v 22 Herodiyas yawarumbuye i mena i ru na i thari. Herod na giyagiyako meth…® rakaruko e thagako th…® warari lagh…®ye le thariko kaiwae. Amba Herod i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThe bigiya nuwaniya ne u naŇčgo e ghino ya wogiya e ghen!‚ÄĚ
\v 23 Amba i tholo iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage e ghen, thebigiya ne u naŇčgoŇča, othembe lo ghamba mbaroke mboro ne ya woveŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Amba wevoko i raŇčgi na ve vaito t…®nae iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya naŇčgo weya budakai kiŇč…®kowe?‚ÄĚ T…®nae i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúJon Rabap…®taiso umbaliye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 E mbaŇčako iyako wevoko i rukunjogha weya kiŇč…®ko na veŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaŇčguiya e mbaŇčake iyake u kitena Jon Rabap…®taiso numwe na u womena umbaliye e gaeba.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Iyake i vakatha KiŇč Herod nuwae i thar…® lagh…®ye moli, ko mava val…®kaiwae i gotena le renuwaŇčako kaiwae kaero me tholo giyagiyako inanji e thagako iyako e maranji.
\v 27 E mbaŇčako iyako i variya le ragagaith…® regha na i dagewe ve wo Jon umbaliye na i woma. Ragagaith…®ko i wa na ve kitena Jon numwe e thiyo t…®ne,
\v 28 amba i womban umbaliye e gaeba, i th…®n…®mena na i th…®n…®giya weya wevoko na ve th…®n…®giya weya t…®nae.
\v 29 MbaŇča Jon gharaghambu th…® loŇčweya iyake, th…® mena th…® wo riwae na th…® beku.
\s1 Jisas i vaghan…®Ňčgiya paeb tausan
\r (Mat 14:13-21; Luk 9:10-17; Jon 6:1-14)
\p 
\v 30 MbaŇča ghal…®Ňčaeko gharaghamb…® va i variyeŇčgima th…® rakanjogha, th…® mevathavatha weinji Jisas, na th…® utugiya lenji vakatha na vavaghareko utuniye.
\v 31 Ghar…®ghar…® th…® ghanagha th…® rakamena na th…® raka. Jisas na gharaghambu ma e ghanjimbaŇča na val…®kaiwae th…® ghan…®Ňčga. Iya kaiwae i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo ra raka e val…®vaŇčga regha, mbe ghinda eŇčge, na wo vara towowe.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 Amba th…® rakatha e waŇčga mbe thiye eŇčge na th…® raka e val…®vaŇčga ma ghar…®ghar…®niye.
\p 
\v 33 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® i ghanagha e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye th…® thuweŇčgi na th…® ghareghare thavalaŇčgiyako, iya kaiwae mbema ghenji na n…®manji eŇčge, th…® raka Ňčgalai e Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye na veth…® vuthakai, muyai amba Jisas na gharaghambu th…® womaru.
\v 34 MbaŇča Jisas i nja e waŇčga na i thuwe wabwi lagh…®ye, ghare i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli kaiwanji kaiwae Ňčgoranjiya sip ma e ghanjiranjimbunjimbu. Iya kaiwae i vavaghareŇča bigibigi i ghanagha weŇčgi.
\v 35 Yegh…®yegh…®ye e mbaŇčako iyako, gharaghambu th…® mena th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKaero yegh…®yegh…®ye moli na vanatherowo iyake.
\v 36 U variyeŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®na, u dage weŇčgi na th…® raka e ghembaghemba nanasiye e val…®vaŇčgake iyake na tembe thiye th…® tamweya ghanji, th…® vamodo na th…® ghan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 37 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi hu giya ghan…®Ňčga weŇčgi na th…® ghan!‚ÄĚ Gharenji i yo lagh…®ye moli na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare nuwaniyaime vo giya mani geth…®seriyeiwo (200) na wo vamodo ghan…®Ňčgawe na wo vaŇčamweŇčgiwe?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 38 Jisas i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBred mbumbuviye na weŇčga? Hu wa na vohu thuwe.‚ÄĚ
\p MbaŇča veth…® thuwe, th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBred mbumbulima na borogi umboiwo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 39 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambuko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®na th…® mevathavatha e wabwi nanasiye na thiya yaku e nanana vwatavwata.‚ÄĚ
\v 40 Ghar…®ghar…®ko thiya yaku wagiyawe e wabwi nanasiye. Wabwi vavana mun…®thaŇčar…® (100) iya na wabwi vavana mun…®yelima (50) iya.
\v 41 Amba Jisas i mban…®Ňčgiya bred…®ko mbumbulimako na borogiko umboiwoko, i gh…®mara voro e buruburu na i vata ago weya Loi ghan…®Ňčgako kaiwae. I njiviyaviya bred…®ko mbumbulimako na i giya weŇčgiya gharaghambuko na th…® giya weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko. Vambe i njiviyaviyava borogiko umboiwo na i giya weŇčgi.
\v 42 Taulagh…®ko thiya ghan…®Ňčga na val…®kaiwanji.
\v 43 Amba gharaghambu th…® mban…®vanjaraŇčgiya nambonambo Ňčgamwayaworo na Ňčgamwaiwo bred na borogiko meth…® ghan…®vareŇčgiko.
\v 44 Gh…®mogh…®moruko va thiya ghan…®Ňčgako lenji ghanaghanagha paeb tausan.\fig Paeb tausan thiya ghan…®Ňčga na val…®kaiwanji|alt="feeding 5,000" src="WA03855b.tif" size="span" copy="UBS (Wade)" ref="6:37-44"\fig*
\s1 Jisas i loŇčga e njigh…® vwatae
\r (Mat 14:23-33; Jon 6:15-21)
\p 
\v 45 Va e mbaŇčako iyako i variyeŇčgiya gharaghambu th…® tha e waŇčga na th…® womaviva e ghamwae Bet…®saida, Galili Njigh…®niye val…®vaŇčga regha na amalagh…®niye wo i variyeŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko na th…® raka.
\v 46 I ghawoloŇčgiyana e ghereiye, i voro e ou ghadidiye na i naŇčgowe.
\v 47 Vama i limomouwo na waŇčgama vama inanji e njigh…®ko ghalughawoghawo na Jisas amba ina vanat…®na ghamberegha.
\v 48 I thuwe gharaghambuko th…® rovur…®gheghe e wodo kaiwae va th…® wodo na i ghemba ndewendeweko ghamwae. Vama ghanono igh…®viya rakaraka Jisas i loŇčga e njigh…® vwatae na i mena weŇčgi. Mbalavama i lareŇča weŇčgi,
\v 49 ko mbaŇča va th…® vaidiya i loŇčgaloŇčga e njigh…®ko vwatae, th…®Ňča eŇčge kaka, iwaeŇčge th…® yaro,
\v 50 kaiwae taulagh…®ko va th…® thuwe na th…® mararu. Ko e mbaŇčako iyako Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTha ghanjigharelagh…®lagh…®! Tha huya mararu! Ghino Jisas!‚ÄĚ
\v 51 Amba i tha e waŇčgako weiyaŇčgi na ndewendeweko i mare. Vama i wo vara gharaghambuko nuwanji,
\v 52 kaiwae othembe va th…® thuwe i mbana bred mbumbulima na i vaŇčamweŇčgiya wabwi lagh…®yewe ma vamba nuwanjiko i rumwaruŇča thela Jisas, kaiwae gharenjiko vamba i vur…®gheghe.
\s1 Jisas i thawariya ghambweghambwera Genesaret
\r (Mat 14:34-36)
\p 
\v 53 Vama th…® golawa val…®mbwa na veth…® goru vanat…®na e ghemba regha idae Genesaret na th…® sowo lenji waŇčgakowe.
\v 54 MbaŇča th…® rakanja e waŇčgako ghar…®ghar…® kaero th…® ghareghare Jisas.
\v 55 Amba ghar…®ghar…® th…® yoruku na th…® raka e ghembaghemba e vanautumako iyako t…®ne, th…® bigiŇčgiya ghambweghambwera weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ghamba ghena na veth…® loŇčwevaidiya Jisas utuniye aŇčga inae na th…® yobigiwe.
\v 56 E the val…®vaŇčga Jisas va ve vuthawe, e ghembaghemba nanasiye na lagh…®lagh…®ye na the val…®vaŇčga ghar…®ghar…® inanjiwe, ghar…®ghar…® th…® bigimenaŇčgiya ghanjiune thiya ghambwera Ňčgora ghamba me vathavatha na th…® naŇčgo vur…®gheghewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare u vatomwe na ghambweghambwerake th…® v…®ghath…®gha ghan…®kwamana mbothiye?‚ÄĚ Thavala va th…® v…®ghath…®, taulagh…®ko riwanji i thovuye.
\c 7
\s1 Loi le mbaro na ghar…®ghar…® ghanjithanavu utuniye
\r (Mat 15:1-9)
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča regha Parisi na mbaro gharavavaghare vavana th…® mena Jerusalem na th…® megh…®liŇča Jisas.
\v 2 Th…® thuweŇčgiya Jisas gharaghambu vavana thiya ghan…®Ňčga mava th…® thavwiya n…®man…®manji Ňčgoreiya ghanjithanavu.
\v 3 Kaiwae thiye Parisi na Jiu taulagh…®ko th…® ghambugha ŇčgoroŇčga orumburumbunji va th…® valawe weŇčgi. Amba mane th…® ghan…®Ňčga ghaghada ne th…® thavwiya n…®manji Ňčgoreiya ghanjithanavu.
\v 4 MbaŇča th…® njogha e ghamba maket, amba mane th…® ghan…®Ňčga ghaghad ne th…® thavwiya ghanjimberegha Ňčgoreiye ghanjithanavuke iyake. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thanavu i ghanagha th…® ghambu th…® mena weŇčgiya orumburumbunji, Ňčgoreiya ndegh…®, uye na gaeba ghanjighethavwi.
\p 
\v 5 Amba Parisi na mbaro gharavavaghare th…® vaito Jisas th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae ghan…®raghambuna ma th…® ghambugha ŇčgoroŇčga orumburumbunda va th…® valawe weinda, iyemaeŇčge ma th…® thavwiya n…®man…®manji kaero thiya ghan…®Ňčga?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúAiseya va i utuŇčake mbema emunjoru. Mamimina ghavwalaiwo Ňčgoreiya va i rori:
\p ‚Äú‚ÄėLoi iŇča ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ke thiyake e ghaenjike njimwae th…® yavwatata wanaŇčgo, ko gharenjiko i bwagabwaga moli e ghino.
\v 7 Ma th…® kururu emunjoru e ghino, th…® vavaghareŇča ghar…®ghar…® lenji renuwaŇča na th…®Ňčava Loi le mbaro.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 7:7 \xt Ais 29:13\x*
\p 
\v 8 Amba Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúHu gheneviyathu Loi le mbaro, na hu vikiki eŇčge mbaroŇčgina iya ghar…®ghar…®na th…® vakatha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Na Jisas i gotubwe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema hu thimba vara, iya hu botewo Loi le mbaroke na hu vikikighath…® eŇčge ghemi ghamivavaghare.
\v 10 Wo hu thuwe! Mosese i giya Loi le mbaro weinda iŇča, ‚ÄėU yavwatata wanaŇčgiya t…®na na rama,‚Äô\x - \xo 7:10 \xt RaŇč 20:12; Mba 5:16; RaŇč 21:17\x* na reghava ‚ÄėThela i utuvathar…® weŇčgiya t…®nae na ramae val…®kaiwae moliya i mare.‚Äô
\v 11 Ko ghemi hu munjeva huŇča i thovuye eŇčge thoŇčgo lolo regha i dage weŇčgiya t…®nae na ramae iŇča: ‚ÄėMa munje ya giya bigibigi vavana weŇčga na i thalavuŇčga, ko mbaŇčake kaero ma dagerawe weya Loi‚Äô.
\v 12 Mane hu vatomwe na te i vakathava bigi regha t…®nae na ramae kaiwanji.\f + \fr 7:12 \ft Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye ghanjithanavuke iyake idae coban. MbaŇča th…® vakatha coban, th…®Ňča lenji mani va Loi le mani le kaiwo kaiwae. Amba ma wo th…® njimbukikiya ramanji na t…®nanji. Ko iyemaeŇčge, ma th…® giya vara lenji mani weya Loi. Th…® vareghare ghanjimberegha kaiwanji.\f*
\v 13 E kamwath…®ke iyake hu vavagharena iya hu valawe weŇčgiya ghamunena huŇčava Loi le mbaro ma e ghathovuye. Na bigibigi th…® ghanagha Ňčgoranjiyake hu vakathaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Budakai i vakathainda na ra thar…® Loi e marae
\r (Mat 15:10-20)
\p 
\v 14 Jisas i kula vathavathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo na mbowo th…® rakamenaweva, na iŇča, ‚ÄúTaulagh…®na ghemi, hu vandeŇčeŇčgo na hu ghareghare budakaiya ne ya utuŇčake weŇčga.
\v 15 Thebigiya ra ghan ma i vamb…®gh…®yainda, ko budakai i raŇčgima e ghaendake, iyake i vamb…®gh…®yainda.‚ÄĚ
\v 16 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo e yanayanawami hu vandeŇče wagiyawe ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke na hu ghareghare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 MbaŇča i iteteŇčaŇčgiya wabwiko na i ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne amba gharaghambuko th…® naŇčgowe na i vamanjamanjalaŇča goghaimba iyako weŇčgi.
\p 
\v 18 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKo amba ma nuwamina i manjamanjalaŇča? Amba ma hu ghareghare, budakai lolo i ghan ma val…®kaiwae i vakatha i mbigh…®?
\v 19 Kaiwae ma venja lolo e ghare, nandere, venja eŇčge e Ňčgamoiye na ve reŇča mbe ele kamwath…® na ve raŇčgi.‚ÄĚ (Iya kaiwae mbema ra ghan…®ŇčgaeŇčge.)
\p 
\v 20 Na mbowo iŇčava, ‚ÄúBudakai i raŇčgima e gharendake, iyako i vamb…®gh…®yainda.
\v 21 Kaiwae i mena maya e gharenda na i raŇčgi, Ňčgoranji: renuwaŇča raraithar…®, vavaghena, kaiv…®, gabo, yathima,
\v 22 votha, vakatha thanavu raithar…®, utu kwan…®kwan, rokiwodowodo, yamwakabu, utu rere, wovorevoreŇča, na unouno.
\v 23 Thanavuke raraithar…® wolagh…®ye thiyake th…® raŇčgima lolo e ghare, thiyake th…® vamb…®gh…®yainda.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Ela ma Jiu le loŇčweghath…®
\r (Mat 15:21-28)
\p 
\v 24 Amba Jisas i iteteŇča ghembako iyako na i wa Taiya ele val…®vaŇčga. I ru e Ňčgolo regha t…®ne na ma nuwaiya lolo regha i ghareghare ina gheko, ko ma val…®kaiwae i kubaro.
\v 25-26 Ela eunda, ma Jiu, va i vir…® Poenisiya ele val…®vaŇčga Siriya e t…®ne. Elako yawarumbuye nyao raithar…® inawe. I loŇčweya Jisas utuniye na i menawe e mbaŇčako iyako i ronja e gheghe vuvuye. I naŇčgo vur…®gheghewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThare val…®kaiwae, u variyeraŇčgiya nyaoko raithar…® yawarumbuŇčgukowe!‚ÄĚ
\v 27 Ko Jisas i utuŇča Jiu utuninji iya iŇčake, ‚ÄúWo ra ŇčamwekaiŇčgiya gamagai. Ma val…®kaiwae ra wo gamagai ghanji na ra wokiyathu weŇčgiya mbughambugha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, othembe mbughambugha th…® ghana gamagai ghanji murimuriye e ghamba ghan…®Ňčga raberabe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Iya kaiwae Jisas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae len gonjoghana len loŇčweghath…® i woraŇčgiya, u njogha e Ňčgolo. Nyaoma raithar…® kaero me raŇčgi weya yawarumbuma.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 I njogha e Ňčgolo na i vaidiya yawarumbuye riwae kaero i thovuye na i ghena e ghamba, nyaoma raithar…® kaero me raŇčgiwe.
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala yanawae // i kule na ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčae
\p 
\v 31 Amba Jisas i iteta Taiya le val…®vaŇčga, i ghathara Saidon na Ghembaghemba Ghembayaworo e lenji val…®vaŇčga na i wa venja Galili Njigh…®niye.
\v 32 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® womenawe amala regha yanawae i kule na ma val…®kaiwae i utu. Th…® naŇčgo vur…®gheghe weya Jisas na i bigiraweya n…®man…®mae e vwatae.
\v 33 Amba Jisas i vaŇčguiteteŇčgiya wabwiko na ghamberegha moli, i bigiraweya n…®mae l…®kel…®keke amalako e yanayanawae na i njoŇčgo na i v…®ghath…® amalako e mamiye.
\v 34 Amba Jisas i gh…®mara voro e buruburu, i momao lagh…®ye na i dage weya amalako iŇča, ‚ÄúEp…®patha,‚ÄĚ gharumwaru, ‚ÄúU mavu!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 35 E mbaŇčako iyako amalako yanayanawae na ghal…®Ňčae th…® mavu amba i utu na ghal…®Ňčae i manjamanjala.
\v 36 Amba Jisas i dageten weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na ne th…® ndeutugiya weya lolo regha. I vur…®gheghe na i dageten weŇčgi, ko mbaŇča regha na regha ma th…® rena th…® utuŇča eŇčge budakaiya me vakatha.
\v 37 Taulagh…®ko iya va th…® vandeŇčeko gharenji i yo lagh…®ye moli, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBigibigike wolagh…®ye amalake iyake i vakathaŇčgi i thovuye. Mbe i thawariŇčgiva ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® loŇčwe na ghar…®ghar…® ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčanji.‚ÄĚ
\c 8
\s1 Jisas i vaghan…®Ňčgiya po tausan
\r (Mat 15:32-39)
\p 
\v 1 Ma va mbaŇča molao e ghereiye wabwi lagh…®ye th…® mevathavatha. Kaiwae ghanji vama iko, Jisas i kula vathaŇčgiya gharaghambu na i dage weŇčgi iŇča,
\v 2 ‚ÄúGhareŇčgu i v…®r…® ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake kaiwanji, kaiwae mbaŇča mbaŇčato weiŇčguyaŇčgi na ghanji kaero iko.
\v 3 ThoŇčgo ya variyeŇčgi na th…® njogha e ghemba na ma ya vaŇčamweŇčgi, ne ghare thavwathavwavo i nja weŇčgi e kamwath…® mborowa kaiwae vavana ghambanji bwagabwaga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Gharaghambu th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAŇčga ne ra vaidiya ghan…®Ňčga lagh…®ye na val…®kaiwae ra vaŇčamweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye thiyake? Vanatherowoke iyake.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Amba Jisas i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBred mbumbuviye na weŇčga?‚ÄĚ Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbumbupir…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 I dage weŇčgiya wabwima na thiya yaku bode. Amba i mbana bred…®ko mbumbupir…®ko na i vata ago weya Loi, i njiviyaviya na i giya weŇčgiya gharaghambuko na th…® giya weŇčgiya wabwima, na gharaghambuko th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye.
\v 7 Vambe e ghanjiborogi nanasiye seiwova. Jisas i vata ago kaiwae na i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambuko tembe th…® giyava.
\v 8 Taulagh…®ko thiya ghan…®Ňčga na val…®kaiwanji. Amba gharaghambuko th…® mban…®Ňčgiya meth…® ghan…®vareŇčgima na th…® mban vanjaraŇčgiya nambonambo Ňčgamwapir…®.
\v 9 Iyava thiya ghan…®Ňčgako gh…®mogh…®moru lenji ghanaghanagha po tausan. Amba i variyeŇčgi na th…® raka,
\v 10 na e mbaŇčako iyako weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu th…® tha e waŇčga na th…® golawa th…® wa Dalamanuta ele val…®vaŇčga.\f + \fr 8:10 \ft Buk Boboma gharaghareghare vavana th…® renuwaŇča Dalamanuta ida reghava Magadan.\f*
\s1 Parisi nuwanjiya Jisas i vakatha vakatha // ghamba rotaele regha na th…® thuwe
\r (Mat 12:38-42; 16:1-4)
\p 
\v 11 MbaŇča Parisi vavana th…® loŇčwevaidiya Jisas ina gheko th…® mena th…® wogaith…® weinji. Va nuwanjiya th…® mando iyava th…® dagewe na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele regha na wo thuwe, na wo ghareghare emunjoru len vur…®gheghena i mena weya Loi o nandere.‚ÄĚ
\v 12 Jisas le renuwaŇča i vuyowo, i th…®n…®njoŇča ghatenuwanuwa, na iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae ghemi thake iyake ghemi nuwami ya vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele regha kaiwami na hu thuwe? Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, mane ya vakatha vakatha regha kaiwami!‚ÄĚ
\v 13 Amba i iteteŇčgi, na ve tha e waŇčgako na ma th…® gonjoghava e val…®vaŇčga regha.
\s1 Parisi na Herod lenji is…®t ghagoghaimba
\r (Mat 16:5-12)
\p 
\v 14 Ko iyemaeŇčge gharaghambu th…® renuwaŇča vaghalawe na ma th…® mbana bred i ghanagha, vambe mbumbura eŇčge ina e waŇčgako.
\v 15 Jisas i dage vavur…®gheghe weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu njimbukiki wagiyawe! Hu njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčga Parisi lenji is…®t na Herod le is…®t kaiwae!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Gharaghambu th…® veutu weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMe utu Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae ma mara ndewo mun bred.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Jisas va i ghareghare gharaghambuko lenji vethoko r…®ghe iwaeŇčge i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae hu veutu weŇčga bred kaiwae? Ko nuwamina mamba i rumwaru? Mbema emunjoru gharemi th…® vuyowo!
\v 18 ‚ÄėMbe e maramarami ‚ÄĒ ma hu thuwe? Na mbe e yanayanawami ‚ÄĒ ma hu loŇčwe?‚Äô\x - \xo 8:18 \xt Jer 5:21\x* Ko ma hu renuwaŇčakiki
\v 19 mbaŇča va ya njiviyaviya bred…®ma mbumbulimama ghar…®ghar…®ma paeb tausan kaiwanji? Nambonambo Ňčgamwaviye va hu mban…®vanjaraŇčgi e ghanjima vaŇčgovaŇčgothiye?‚ÄĚ Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägamwayaworo na Ňčgamwaiwo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 Na i gotubwe iŇča, ‚ÄúNa mbaŇča va ya njiviyaviya bred…®ma mbumbupir…®ma ghar…®ghar…®ma po tausan…®ma kaiwanji, nambonambo Ňčgamwaviye va hu mban…®vanjaraŇčgi e ghan…®Ňčgama vaŇčgovaŇčgothiye?‚ÄĚ Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägamwapir…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKo amba ma nuwamina i rumwaru? Iya vakathaŇčgiko ghamba rotaele va ya vakathaŇčgiko th…® woraŇčgiya ya mena weya Loi.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala marae i kwaghe Bet…®saida
\p 
\v 22 Amba va th…® womaru eŇčge Bet…®saida kaero ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® womena amala marae i kwaghe weya Jisas th…® naŇčgo vur…®gheghewe i v…®ghath…® na marae kaero i thovuye.
\v 23 Jisas i vaŇčgwa amalako maraeko i kwaghe e n…®mae na i vaŇčguiteta ghembako. I njoŇčgovuna marae amba i yabo e n…®man…®maeko na mbaŇča i ban kaero i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThare u thuwe bigi regha?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Amalako kaero i thuwe na iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, ya thuweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® ko ghanjithuwathuwa Ňčgoreiya umbwaumbwama, th…® rakaraka loloŇčga eŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Jisas mbowo i bigiraweva n…®man…®mae amalako e maramarae. MbaŇčaniye i gh…®maratako i thuwe wagiyaweŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye, maramaraeko kaero th…® thovuyeva.
\v 26 Jisas i variye i wa ele Ňčgolo na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe u ndewa e ghembana t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pita iŇča Jisas iye Krais
\r (Mat 16:13-20; Luk 9:18-21)
\p 
\v 27 Amba Jisas na gharaghambu th…® raka e ghembaghemba nanasiye Sisariya Pilipai ghadidiye. I vaitoŇčgi e kamwath…® mborowa iŇča, ‚ÄúKo ghar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča thela ghino?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVavana th…®Ňča Jon Rabap…®taiso, vavana th…®Ňča Ilaija na vavana th…®Ňča Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu regha i njoghama.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Amba i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNa ghemi huŇča thela ghino?‚ÄĚ Pita i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Krais ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Jisas i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgiya gharaghambuko na ne th…® ndeutugiya weya lolo regha, thela amalagh…®niye.
\s1 Jisas i utuŇča le mare utuniye mbaŇčaiwoniye
\r (Mat 16:21-28; Luk 9:22-27)
\p 
\v 31 Jisas i utuŇča le mare utuutuniye weŇčgiya gharaghambu iŇča, ‚ÄúLolo Nariye ghino ne ya vaidiŇčgiya vuyowo i ghanagha na Jiu lenji randeviva, ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare ne th…® botewoŇčgo, na ne th…® tagavamareŇčgo, na mbaŇča theghetoninji e t…®ne kaero ya thuweiruva.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 Va i vamanjamanjalaŇča wagiyawe weŇčgiya iya utuke iyake. Amba Pita i vaŇčguiteteŇčgiya ghauneko na i dageten…®we thava i utuŇčaŇčgiya utuutu ŇčgoranjiŇčgiyako.
\v 33 Amba Jisas i ndev…® na i thuweŇčgiya gharaghambuko, na i Ňčael…®mbiya weya Pita iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena e ghereiŇčguke, Seitan! Len renuwaŇčana ma i reŇča Loi ele renuwaŇča, i reŇča ghar…®ghar…® e lenji renuwaŇča.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 Amba Jisas i kula vathavathaŇčgiya wabwiko lagh…®ye weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo thela nuwaiya i ghambuŇčgo, tembe ghamberegha i botewo iya nuwaeko nuwaiya i vakatha na i wovaira ghakros na i wo, amba i ghambuŇčgo othembe vuyowo o mare.
\v 35 Kaiwae thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya i vamora yawaliye, ne i th…®vaghawa yawaliye, ko thela thoŇčgo i vatomweya yawaliye ghino kaiwaŇčgu na Toto Thovuye kaiwae ne i vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye.
\v 36 ŇägoroŇčga ghathovuye thoŇčgo lolo regha i wo yambaneke lagh…®ye na i mbaroŇča, ko iyemaeŇčge i th…®vaiya yawal…® memeghabananiye?
\v 37 Ne i wo budakai na i vamodanjogha yawaliyekowe? Nandere moli!
\v 38 Kaiwae thoŇčgo lolo regha i monjina wanaŇčgo na i monjina wanaŇčgiya ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke e thake iya ragoriwoyathu na unounoke thiyake e t…®nenji, Ghino Lolo Nariye tembene ya monjinawanava mbaŇča ne ya njoghama weiŇčgu Bwebwe le vwenyevwenye na weiŇčguyaŇčgiya nyao boboma.‚ÄĚ
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, ghar…®ghar…® vavana inanji gheke amba muyai th…® mare wone th…® thuweya Loi le mbaroko ghavur…®gheghe i woraweya r…®ghe.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas ghayamoyamo i ghenevagh…®le
\r (Mat 17:1-13; Luk 9:28-36)
\p 
\v 2 MbaŇča theghewona e ghereiye Jisas i vaŇčguŇčgiya Pita, Jemes na Jon, i viva weŇčgi, na th…® voro e ou molao regha mbe thiye eŇčge. E maranji, Jisas ghayamoyamo i ghenevagh…®le,
\v 3 ghakwama i kaleva moli na i ndalandala. Le kakaleva i kivwala thela e yambaneke ne i thavwiya kwama na le kakaleva.
\v 4 Amba gharaghambuko theghetoko th…® thuweŇčgiya Ilaija na Mosese th…® yomara, th…® utu weinji Jisas.
\p 
\v 5 Pita i dage weya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, i thovuye eŇčge vara inanda gheke. Ne wo vakathaŇčgiya yoŇčathowathowa Ňčgoloto, Ňčgolora ghen, Ňčgolora Mosese na Ňčgolora Ilaija.‚ÄĚ
\v 6 I utu Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae va th…® mararu lagh…®ye, Pita mava i ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga me utu na iŇča.
\p 
\v 7 Amba Ňčgal…®l…® ghambaghambaluwae i ganaŇčgi na ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha i mena e Ňčgal…®l…®ko e t…®ne iŇča, ‚ÄúIyake NaruŇčgu, val…®ghareghareŇčgu moli. Hu vandeŇče wagiyawe.‚ÄĚ
\v 8 E mbaŇčako iyako th…® gh…®maratako, ko mava te th…® thuweva lolo regha, Jisas ghamberegha.
\p 
\v 9 MbaŇča va th…® njamanjama e ouko, Jisas i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNe hu ndeutugiya weya lolo regha iya bigiko mohu thuweko, ghaghada Lolo Nariye ne i thuweiru e mare t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Th…® ghambugha ghal…®Ňčama na vambe thiye eŇčge th…® vevaitoŇčgi ŇčgoroŇčga ‚Äúthuweiru e mare‚ÄĚ gharumwaru.
\p 
\v 11 Amba th…® vaito Jisas th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mbaro gharavavaghare th…®Ňča Ilaija ne i menakai amba muyai Mesaiya i mena?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru Ilaija ne i menakai na i vanamwe bigibigike wolagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge, buda kaiwae buk iŇča Lolo Nariye ne i vaidiya vuyowo lagh…®ye na th…® botewoyathu?
\v 13 Ko ya dage e ghemi, Ilaija kaerova i mena na ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakatha thambo renuwaŇča nuwanjiya th…® vakathawe, Ňčgoreiya Buk Boboma Teuye le govambwara amalagh…®niye kaiwae.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i thawariya thegha nyao raithar…® inawe
\r (Mat 17:14-21; Luk 9:37-43)
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča Jisas na gharaghambuko theghetoko th…® vutha weŇčgiya gharaghambuma vavana, th…® thuwe wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rogh…®liŇčaŇčgi na mbaro gharavavaghare vavana. Va th…® wogaith…® weinjiyaŇčgi.
\v 15 MbaŇča ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® thuwe Jisas, gharenji i yo lagh…®ye moli, th…® rukuwe na th…® dage mwaewowe.
\v 16 Amba Jisas i vaitoŇčgiya gharaghambuko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wogaith…®Ňča budakai weimiyaŇčgiya mbaro gharavavaghare?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Amala regha e wabwiko t…®ne i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, ma vaŇčgumena naruŇčguke e ghen kaiwae nyao raithar…® inawe na ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčae.
\v 18 ThembaŇča nyaoko raithar…® i mbaroŇča, i wokiyathu e thelau vwatae, njoŇčgonjoŇčgo i raŇčgi e ghae, i r…®gh…®mbiya ŇčiŇčiye na riwaeko lagh…®ye th…® gheroro. Ma naŇčgo weŇčgiya ghan…®raghambuke na th…® dage weya nyaoke raithar…® i raŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge ma val…®kaiwanji meth…® vakatha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi ma e lemi loŇčweghath…®! ŇägoroŇčga mbaŇča le molamolao wo ya yaku weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi? ŇägoroŇčga mbaŇča le molamolao ya ghataŇčaghath…®Ňčga? Hu vaŇčgumena weŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Th…® vaŇčgumena theghako weya Jisas. MbaŇča nyaoko raithar…® i thuwe Jisas, i vakatha theghako na riwae i mwanavatha na i dobu e thelauko vwatae na i bulabulale loloŇčga na njoŇčgonjoŇčgo i raŇčgi e ghae.
\v 21 Jisas i vaito ramae iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga mbaŇča le molamolao nyaoko raithar…® le yaku weya theghako?‚ÄĚ I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúVambe Ňčgama vara.
\v 22 MbaŇča i ghanagha nyaoma raithar…® i mando na i un…®gh…®, i wokiyathu e nd…®ghe une o e mbwa t…®ne. U gharev…®r…®Ňčaime na u thalavuime, thoŇčgo val…®kaiwan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga len utuna gharumwaru, moŇčana, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo val…®kaiwan‚Äô? Kaiwae bigibigike wolagh…®ye val…®kaiwae weya thelolo i loŇčweghath…®gha Loi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Ňägamako ramae e mbaŇčako iyako i utu na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúYa loŇčweghath…®, ko ma i lagh…®ye. U thalavuŇčgo na lo loŇčweghath…®ke i lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 MbaŇča Jisas vama i thuweŇčgiya wabwiko ma i lagh…®ye eŇčge, i dage weya nyaoko raithar…® iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen kule na kwaghe nyaoniye, ya dage e ghen na u raŇčgima weya theghana na ma tene u ruweva mbaŇča regha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Nyaoko raithar…® i yaro i vandindiya theghako riwae na i raŇčgi. Ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya i mare, iya kaiwae th…® ghanagha th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúI mare.‚ÄĚ
\v 27 Ko Jisas i v…®ghath…®gha theghako n…®mae, i thalavu na i thuweiru, na i yondovir…®.
\p 
\v 28 Iyake e ghereiye Jisas i ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne. Gharaghambuko th…® vaito thuwele th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae ma val…®kaiwae mo variyeraŇčgiya nyaoko raithar…®?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhakamwath…® mbereghaeŇčge, thoŇčgo nuwamiya hu variyeraŇčgiya nyao raithar…® Ňčgoreiyako, wo hu naŇčgo weya Loi.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas mbowo i utuŇčava le mare na le thuweiruva
\r (Mat 17:22-23; Luk 9:43b-45)
\p 
\v 30 Jisas na gharaghambu th…® iteta val…®vaŇčgako iyako na th…® ghathara Galili. Jisas ma nuwaiya lolo regha i ghareghare aŇčga inae,
\v 31 kaiwae i vavaghare weŇčgiya gharaghambuko iŇča: ‚ÄúLolo Nariye ne th…® yalawe na th…® un…®gh…®. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča mbaŇčatoniye e t…®ne kaero i thuweiruva.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 Ko iyemaeŇčge ma nuwanji i manjamanjala ŇčgoroŇčga le vavaghareko gharumwaru, na th…® mararu th…® vaito amalagh…®niye.
\s1 Thela lagh…®ye moli
\r (Mat 18:1-5; Luk 9:46-48)
\p 
\v 33 Amba Jisas na gharaghambu th…® raka mena Kapenaom, na mbaŇča vama th…® ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne amba i vaitoŇčgiya gharaghambuko iŇča, ‚ÄúMohu wogaith…®Ňča buda kaiwae e kamwath…®ko mborowa?‚ÄĚ
\v 34 E lenji loŇčga mborowae meth…® wogaith…®Ňča thela ina e t…®nenjiko iye lagh…®ye, iya kaiwae th…® monjina na th…® rokubaro.
\p 
\v 35 Jisas i yaku na i kula vathavathaŇčgiya gharaghambuko theyaworo na theghewoko na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo thela nuwaiya i tabona lagh…®ye Loi e marae tembe i wonjoŇča ghamberegha na i muyai moli, na i tabo na rakakaiwo weŇčgiya ghauneko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 36 Jisas i vaŇčgwa Ňčgama nasiye regha na i vaŇčgurawe i ndeghath…® e t…®nenji. I tagavagaghala n…®mae Ňčgamako e mborowae amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča,
\v 37 ‚ÄúThela thoŇčgo i kulavatha Ňčgama regha Ňčgora iyake e idaŇčgu, iye i kulavathaŇčgo; na thela thoŇčgo i kulavathaŇčgo, mambe i kulavatha eŇčge ghino, tembe i kulavathava thela i variyeŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Thela ma i botewoinda iye ghandau
\r (Luk 9:49-50)
\p 
\v 38 Jon i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, wo vaidiya amala regha i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® e idan. Na wo mando na wo dageten…®we kaiwae iye ma weinda.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 39 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThava hu dageten…®we, kaiwae ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha i vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele regha e idaŇčgu na e mbaŇčako iyako kaero i utuŇčava utu raraithar…® kaiwaŇčgu.
\v 40 Kaiwae thela ma iye ghandath…®gh…®ya iye ghandau.
\v 41 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, thela thoŇčgo i th…®n…®giya mbwa e ghemi na hu mun kaiwae ghemi woraghambu, emunjoru ne e modamodae.‚ÄĚ
\s1 ThoŇčgo lolo i vakatha lolo regha i vakatha thar…®
\r (Mat 18:6-9)
\p 
\v 42 I gotubwe na iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ra wo var…® lagh…®ye na ra Ňčgara loloko iyako e numwe na ra wokiyathu e Ňčambuwoko t…®ne, lith…®ko iyako i lagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi ne i giya lolo regha ghalith…® i lagh…®ye moli thoŇčgo i vakatha Ňčgama Ňčgoreiyake regha i vakatha thar…® na ma i loŇčweghath…®Ňčgo.
\v 43 Na thoŇčgo n…®man…®na i vakathaŇčge na u vakatha thar…®, u kiten…®yathu! I thovuye moli thoŇčgo n…®man regha nandere na u vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye, na thava n…®man…®man…®na theghewona na u wa vo ru Gehena, e nd…®gheko iya i meghabanako e t…®ne.
\v 44 E ghembako iyako uleulema iya th…® uleŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ma mane th…® mare, na nd…®ghema iya th…® ndamawe mane mbaŇča regha i mare.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 9:44 \ft R…®ghethoru 44,46 na 48 th…® govambwara Loi ghal…®Ňčae ina Ais 66:24. Iyake i utuŇča ŇčgoroŇčga ne iŇča na Loi i lith…® weŇčgiya ghath…®gh…®yaŇčgiko gheko.\f*
\p 
\v 45 ‚ÄúNa thoŇčgo gheghen…®na regha i vakathaŇčge na u vakatha thar…®, u kiten…®yathu! I thovuye moli thoŇčgo gheghen regha nandere na u vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye, na thava gheghen…®na theghewo na veth…® wokiyathu ruwoŇčge Gehena e t…®ne.
\v 46 E ghembako iyako uleulema iya th…® uleŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ma mane th…® mare, na nd…®ghema iya th…® ndamawe mane mbaŇča regha i mare.
\v 47 Na thoŇčgo maran…®na regha i vakathaŇčge na u vakatha thar…®, u vovavuthuyathu! I thovuye eŇčge thoŇčgo vo ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro wein maran…®na vogh…®ra eŇčge, na thava maramaran…®na vogh…®wo na veth…® wokiyathuruwoŇčge Gehena.
\v 48 E ghembako iyako uleulema iya th…® uleŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ma mane th…® mare, na nd…®ghema iya th…® ndamawe mane mbaŇča regha i mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 49 Jisas mbowo i utuŇčava ghanjithanavu kaiwae iŇča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ne th…® gham…®no tomethi vuyowo lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya nd…®ghe, na thiyake th…® woraŇčgiya ghanjithanavu, i thovuye o i thar…®. Ňägoreiya vowo th…® woraweya njigh…® na i vanamwe na i th…®na.\f + \fr 9:49 \ft Loi i vakaiwoŇča mandoŇčgike thiyake na i vaemunjoruŇča thavala le ghar…®ghar…® emunjoru, i vanamweŇčgi na i vavur…®ghegheŇča le v…®ghath…® weiyaŇčgi (Ais 48:10; Rom 5:3-5; Jem 1:2-4; 1Pit 1:6-7).\f*
\v 50 Njigh…® iye i thovuye, ko thoŇčgo njigh…®ko gham…®nae ma Ňčgoreiya njigh…®, ma te kamwath…® reghava na val…®kaiwae ra vakatha na gham…®nae i njogha. Iya kaiwae ghamithanavu ne Ňčgoreiye njigh…® mbe e gham…®gham…®nae na ghemi regha na regha hu yaku na ghamwami vanaora weimiyaŇčgiya ghamunena.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 9:50 \ft Njigh…® va ghakaiwo i ghanagha Buk Boboma e ghambaŇča t…®ne. Iye va bigi lagh…®ye regha. ‚ÄúHu wo njigh…®‚ÄĚ iye utu Ňčande regha. Gharumwaru thiya: ‚ÄúHu yakuŇča Loi le thimba.‚ÄĚ o ‚ÄúRegha na regha hu verabi weŇčga.‚ÄĚ o ‚ÄúHu veghan giya ghami.‚ÄĚ o ‚ÄúHu yakuŇča yawal…® iya i thalavuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®na.‚ÄĚ\f*
\c 10
\s1 Ghe na yawo utuninji
\r (Mat 5:31-32; 19:1-12; Luk 16:18)
\p 
\v 1 Amba Jisas i iteteŇča ghembako iyako na i wa Judiya ele val…®vaŇčga amba ve lawa e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan na i wa val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro. Wabwi lagh…®ye mbowo th…® raka menaweva na i vavaghare weŇčgi Ňčgora mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye i vakavakathama.
\p 
\v 2 Parisi vavana th…® menawe na th…® munje th…® mando. Th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare la mbaro i vatomweya amala regha na i yawo weiye levo?‚ÄĚ
\v 3 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi e vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThe mbaro Mosese va i giya weŇčga?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMosese i vatomweya amala i liya yawo ghapeipa i vakatha na i ligiya weya levo na i variyeyathu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMosese va i roriya mbaroke iyake kaiwami kaiwae gharemina i vur…®gheghe.
\v 6 Ko hu renuwaŇčakiki e r…®ghendako, mbaŇča Loi va i vakatha yambaneke na buruburu, i vakatha gh…®moru na wevo.\x - \xo 10:6 \xt R…®gh 1:27\x*
\v 7 Na ‚ÄėIyake kaiwae gh…®moru i iteteŇčaŇčgiya ramae na t…®nae, i tubwe weiye levo,
\v 8 na theghewoko th…® tabo na ririwo regha.‚Äô\x - \xo 10:8 \xt R…®gh 2:24\x* Ma te th…® tabo na theghewova, nandere, th…® tabo na regha moli.
\v 9 Iya kaiwae budakaiya Loi vama i tubwe, thava te lolo reghava i rakayathu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 MbaŇča th…® njogha th…® ru e Ňčgoloko t…®ne gharaghambu th…® vaito bigike iyake kaiwae.
\v 11 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo lolo regha i yawo weiye levo na kaero i vaŇčguva wevo eunda iye kaero i yathima.
\v 12 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, thoŇčgo wevo eunda i yawo weiye le gh…®moru na kaero i vaŇčguva gh…®moru regha iye kaero i yathima.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas na gamagai nanasiye
\r (Mat 19:13-15; Luk 18:15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana va th…® bigimenaŇčgiya gamagai weya Jisas na i v…®ghath…®Ňčgi e n…®man…®mae na i naŇčgo kaiwanji, ko iyemaeŇčge gharaghambuko th…® ŇčaevwaŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iya th…® bigimenaŇčgiko.
\v 14 MbaŇča Jisas i loŇčweya iyake ghare i gaith…® wanaŇčgi na i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambuko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vatomweŇčgi na th…® rakamena weŇčgo, thava hu dageten…®Ňčgi, kaiwae Loi le ghamba mbaro ina weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ňčgoranjiya thiyena.
\v 15 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, thela ma i wo Loi le mbaro Ňčgoreiya Ňčgama, mane i ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\v 16 Amba i mban…®Ňčgi i bigiraweya n…®man…®mae e riwanji na i naŇčgo weya Ramae ghare weŇčgi.\fig Jisas weiyaŇčgiya gamagai nanasiye|alt="Jisas with the children" src="Mat19.13.tif" size="span" copy="UBS (GNR)" ref="10:13-16"\fig*
\s1 Amala i vwenyevwenye
\r (Mat 19:16-30; Luk 18:18-30)
\p 
\v 17 MbaŇča Jisas vama ve loŇčgaloŇčga amba amala regha i rukuŇča, i ronja e gheghe vuvuye e ghamwae na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare thovuye, ne ya vakatha budakai na ya vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae uŇča ghino ya thovuye? Ma lolo regha i thovuye, Loi ghamberegha moli.
\v 19 Len vaitona kaiwae, u ghareghare Mosese le mbaro ŇčgoroŇčga iŇča: ‚ÄėTha u gabo, tha u yathima, tha u kaiv…®, tha u wonjowe bwagabwaga, tha u valogha lolo nuwae mbala u mban le bigibigi, u yavwatata wanaŇčgiya rama na t…®na.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 10:19 \xt RaŇč 20:12-16\x*
\p 
\v 20 Amalako i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, mbaŇča vamba thegha vara ghino kaero ya ghambuŇčgiya mbarona thiyena.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Jisas i vonjimbughath…® na gharewe, amba iŇča, ‚ÄúMa bigi regha eŇčge ne u vakatha. U wa na vo vakuneŇčaŇčgiya len bigibigina wolagh…®ye na u giya manina weŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu. Amba ne u vwenyevwenye e buruburu, amba u njoghama na u ghambuŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 MbaŇča amalako i loŇčweya iyake, ghamwae i raraŇčg…®laŇčg…®la weiye le nuwathar…®, kaiwae le gogomwau i lagh…®ye moli.
\p 
\v 23 Amba Jisas i gh…®mara gh…®liŇčaŇčgiya gharaghambuko kaero i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúI vuyowo moli weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® vwenyevwenye lenji ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Gharaghambuko gharenji i yo utuutuko thiyako kaiwanji, ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas mbowo i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúLo ŇčgaŇčga, i vuyowo moli weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.
\v 25 I vuyowo moli weya kamel na i komughathara e nyil…® yathiye, ko i vuyowo lagh…®ye moli weya lolo ravwenyevwenye le ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Amba gharaghambuko gharenji i yo lagh…®ye moli na th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThela eŇčge ne i vaidiya vamoru!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 Jisas marae i ghembeŇčgi na i gonjogha iŇča, ‚ÄúLolo ma val…®kaiwae ne i vamora ghamberegha; ko Loi val…®kaiwae i vakatha, kaiwae Loi val…®kaiwae i vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Amba Pita i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, wo iteteŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye na wo ghambuŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, na ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, thelolo i iteteŇča ghambae, oghaghae, olouye, t…®nae, ramae, le ŇčgaŇčga o le thelau idaŇčgu kaiwae na Toto Thovuye kaiwae,
\v 30 ne i vaidiya lagh…®ye moli e mbaŇčake thiyake. Ne i vaidiya le ŇčgoloŇčgolo, oghaghae, oloulouye, ot…®nat…®nae, le ŇčgaŇčga na le thelau th…® ghanagha na i lagh…®ye moli ‚ÄĒ na weiye bigibigike thiyake tembene ghar…®ghar…® th…® botewova na th…® vakatha vathar…®we, amba mbaŇča ne i menamenako i vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye.
\v 31 Ko thavala noroke th…® lagh…®ye na th…® viva ne th…® muyai na thavala noroke th…® nasiye na th…® muyai ne th…® viva.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i utuŇča le mare utuniye mbaŇčatoninji
\r (Mat 20:17-19; Luk 18:31-34)
\p 
\v 32 Amba Jisas na gharaghambu inanji e kamwath…® i voro Jerusalem; i viva gharaghambuko e ghamwanji. Gharenji i yo lagh…®ye; na ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® raka reghambako th…® mararu. E mbaŇčako iyako i vaŇčguŇčgiya gharaghambuko theyaworo na theghewoko na i utu thuwele weŇčgi budakai ne i yomarawe.
\v 33 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vandeŇče, ra rakavoro Jerusalem na gheko lolo regha ne i vatomwe Lolo Nariye weŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare, ne th…® vakatha ghambaro le mare kaiwae, amba th…® vaŇčgugiya weŇčgiya thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye,
\v 34 na th…® vatabweyaruŇča, th…® njoŇčgo vun, th…® Ňčge na th…® tagavamare; ko mbaŇča theghetoniye e t…®ne kaero i thuweiru na e yawayawaliyeva.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jemes na Jon nuwanjiya th…® mbaro weinji Jisas
\r (Mat 20:20-28)
\p 
\v 35 Amba Jemes na Jon, Sebedi le ŇčgaŇčga, th…® mena weya Jisas na th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, nuwameiya u vakatha bigi regha kaiwame.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 36 Jisas i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwamiya ya vakatha budakai kaiwami?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 37 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne ghan…®mbaŇča u mbaro weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, ne u vatomwe weime, thamaghewoke, na wo yaku weime ghen, regha e unena na regha e moina na wo mbaro weime ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 38 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMa hu ghareghare budakaiya hu naŇčgona. Val…®kaiwamiya hu muna v…®r…®ke ghakom iya ghino ne ya mun…®kewe? Na val…®kaiwamiya ne hu bap…®taiso Ňčgora ne ghino ya bap…®taisoke, e v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli na mare?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 39 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye. Val…®kaiwame eŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p Iya kaiwae Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru ne hu muna v…®r…®ke ghakom Ňčgoreiya ghino ya mun na hu bap…®taiso e v…®r…® lagh…®ye na mare Ňčgoreiye ghino.
\v 40 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghino ma val…®kaiwae ya tuthiya thela ne i yaku e uneŇčguke na thela i yaku e moiŇčguke mbaŇča ne ya mbaro. Ghamba yakuŇčgike thiyake Loi ne i wogiya weŇčgiya thavala va i vivathanawe kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 41 MbaŇča gharaghambuko theyaworo th…® loŇčweya iyake gharenji i gaith…®wanaŇčgiya Jemes na Jon.
\v 42 Amba Jisas i kula vathaŇčgiya gharaghambuko wolagh…®ye na iŇča, ‚ÄúHu ghareghare, thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji rambarombaro th…® mbaroŇčaŇčgi na lenji randeviva lenji vur…®gheghe i vikikiŇčgi.
\v 43 Ko ghemi thava Ňčgoramiya iyako. Thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya iye lolo lagh…®ye e t…®nemina, iye wo i tabo na lemi rakakaiwo.
\v 44 Na thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya i ndeviva weŇčga wo i tabo na lemi rakakaiwobwaga.
\v 45 Mbe Ňčgoreiyeva Lolo Nariye, mava i mena na mbala th…® kaiwo kaiwae, ko i mena na i kaiwo ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji, i vatomweya yawaliye, i vamodonjoghaŇčgi e lenji thar…® t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i thawariya Batimiyos maramarae
\r (Mat 20:29-34; Luk 18:35-43)
\p 
\v 46 Jisas na gharaghambu kaero th…® vutha Jeriko na mbaŇča vama th…® warewareri vara weinjiyaŇčgiya wabwi lagh…®ye, kaero amala maramarae th…® kwaghe na vata le naŇčgo, idae Batimiyos, Timiyos nariye, vambe i yaku e kamwath…®ko ghadidiye.
\p 
\v 47 MbaŇča i loŇčweya Jisas rara Nasaret iya i reŇča e ghadidiye, ko amba i kula iŇča, ‚ÄúJisas! Deivid rumbuye! Gharen i njaoweŇčgo!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 48 Ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo th…® marakawana na th…® dagewe i towo. Ko iyemaeŇčge i kula na ghal…®Ňčae ma lagh…®ye eŇčge iŇča, ‚ÄúDeivid rumbuye, gharen i njaoweŇčgo!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 49 Jisas i ndeghath…® kaero iŇča, ‚ÄúHu kulamawe na i mena.‚ÄĚ
\p Kaero ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® kula weya amalako maramarako th…® kwaghe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNuwan i loghe! U yondo vir…®! I kula e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 50 I liyathu ghakwama ghayaboyabo, i yondopito na i mena weya Jisas.
\p 
\v 51 Amba Jisas i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaniya ya vakatha budakai kaiwan?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, nuwaŇčguiya maramaraŇčguke th…® thovuye na ma ya thuweva.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 52 Jisas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa, maramaran…®na kaero th…® thovuye kaiwae u loŇčweghath…®.‚ÄĚ
\p E mbaŇčako iyako, Batimiyos kaero i thuweva na i rereghamba weya Jisas e kamwath…®ko.
\c 11
\s1 Jisas i ru Jerusalem
\r (Mat 21:1-11; Luk 19:28-40; Jon 12:12-19)
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča vama th…® vur…®thaiya Jerusalem, Betepage na Betani ghadidinji, Oliv…® e ghanji Ou, Jisas i variyeŇčgiya gharaghambu theghewo e ghamwanji,
\v 2 na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa e ghembana e ghamwamina. MbaŇčaniye vara vohu ru gheko, ne hu vaidiya doŇč…®ki nariye th…® Ňčgar…®rawe na ma mbaŇča regha lolo i thawe. Hu raka na hu vaŇčgumena gheke.
\v 3 ThoŇčgo lolo regha i vaitoŇčga na iŇča, ‚ÄėBuda kaiwae hu vakathake?‚Äô hu dagewe huŇča, ‚ÄėGiya nuwaiya na tene i variye njoghamava gheke mbaŇča ubotu.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Kaero th…® wa na veth…® vaidiya doŇčkima nariye e kamwath…® ghadidiye, th…® Ňčgar…® e Ňčgolo ghath…®n…®mba. Th…® rakaraka ghathiyoko,
\v 5 na ghar…®ghar…® vavana inanji gheko th…® vaitoŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúHu vakatha budakai hu raka doŇčkina nariye?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Th…® gonjogha weŇčgi Ňčgoreiya ŇčgoroŇčga Jisas me utugiyama weŇčgi, na ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® viyathuŇčgi na th…® wa.
\v 7 Th…® vaŇčgumena doŇčkiko weya Jisas, th…® bigiyathu ghanjikwama ghayaboyabo e thetheghan…®ko vwatae na Jisas i thawe.
\v 8 Ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo th…® bigiraweŇčgiya ghanjikwama ghayaboyabo e kamwath…®ko marae na vavana th…® bigiraweya umbwaumbwa yaŇčgayaŇčga e ndamwandamwanji meth…® ten…®Ňčgi e umauma t…®nenji.
\v 9 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® raka viva na vavana th…® raka reghamba th…® yaro na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúHosana! Loi ghare weya amalagh…®niye iya i mena Giya e idaeke.
\v 10 Loi ghare weya Deivid rumbuye iya i menake na i mbaro weinda! Hosana Ramevoro Moliwe.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 11:10 \xt Sam 118:25-26\x*
\p 
\v 11 MbaŇča vama i vutha Jerusalem, i wa ve ru e Ňägolo Boboma na i thuweŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge vama yegh…®yegh…®ye moli weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambuko theyaworo na theghewo th…® raka Betani.
\s1 Jisas i gura umbwa idae fig
\r (Mat 21:18-19)
\p 
\v 12 Va i gh…®viya, th…® ri Betani na th…® njogha Jerusalem, bada i ghara Jisas.
\v 13 I thuwe umbwa regha idae fig. Vamba ina bwagabwaga na i thuwe ndamwandamwaeko i poku moli. I wa na ve kelaŇča thoŇčgo e uneune. MbaŇča i mena e r…®ghe na i thuwe mbe ndamwandamwa eŇčge, kaiwae ma vamba ghambaŇča rau.
\v 14 Jisas i dage weya umbwako iŇča, ‚ÄúMa tene lolo regha i ghan…®va unen mbaŇča regha!‚ÄĚ Gharaghambuko va th…® loŇčweya iya utuutuko iyako.
\s1 Jisas i ru Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne
\r (Mat 21:12-17; Luk 19:45-48; Jon 2:13-22)
\p 
\v 15 MbaŇča th…® vutha Jerusalem, Jisas ve ru e Ňägolo Boboma ghayayao t…®ne na i vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiya thavala th…® vavamodo na th…® vavakune e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne. I mwana vevewoŇčgiya yao gharaten lenji tebol na bunebune gharakune lenji ghamba yaku.
\v 16 I dageten weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na thava te th…® bigighatharava bigi regha kune kaiwae e Ňägolo Boboma ghayayaoko t…®ne.
\v 17 Amba Jisas i vavaghare weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® iŇča, ‚ÄúVa th…® rori Buk Boboma e t…®ne, Loi iŇča, ‚ÄėLo Ňčgolo ne th…® uno idae Ňčgolo ghamba naŇčgo, ghar…®ghar…® e vanautumake wolagh…®ye kaiwanji.‚Äô\x - \xo 11:17 \xt Ais 56:7\x* Ko ghemi hu vakatha Ňčgoreiye rakaiv…® lenji ghamba kubaro!‚ÄĚ\fig Jisas i vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®|alt="Jisas chases out sellers" src="IB04118bw.tif" size="span" copy="Faadil" ref="11:15-17"\fig*
\p 
\v 18 MbaŇča ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare th…® loŇčweya iyake, th…® tamweya kamwath…® ne ŇčgoroŇčga na th…® un…®gha Jisas. Ko kaiwae le vavaghareko va i wo wabwiko nuwanji i vakatha ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare th…® mararu Jisas.
\p 
\v 19 Vama yegh…®yegh…®ye, Jisas na gharaghambu th…® iteta Jerusalem.
\s1 Loi ghaloŇčweghath…®
\r (Mat 21:20-22)
\p 
\v 20 MbaŇčambaŇča vena th…® loŇčgaloŇčga e kamwath…®ko Jerusalem kaiwae amba th…® thuweya fig…®ko i mare, i ri e ndamwae na ve nja e wathewatheliliye.
\v 21 Pita i renuwaŇčakikiya menda Jisas le utuutuma kaero i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, wo u thuwe, umbwako menda u gurako kaero i mareyawowo!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu loŇčweghath…®gha Loi.
\v 23 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, thela ne i dage weya ouke iyake na i wa ve dobu e njigh…®ko t…®ne na ma i numoghegheiwo e ghare, ko iyemaeŇčge i loŇčweghath…®gha ŇčgoroŇčga meŇča ne i yomara, ne Ňčgoreiye.
\v 24 Iya kaiwae ya dage e ghemi: MbaŇča ne hu naŇčgo weya Loi na hu naŇčgowe bigi regha kaiwae, hu loŇčweghath…® emunjoru ne hu vaidi. ThoŇčgo hu vakatha Ňčgoreiye, Loi ne i wogiya weŇčga.
\v 25 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča hu naŇčgo, hu numoyathu lolo regha le thar…® e ghemi, ambane Ramami e buruburu i numotena lemi thar…®.
\v 26 Ko iyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo ma hu numoyathuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana lenji thar…®, mane Ramami e buruburu i numotena lemi thar…®Ňčgina.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas le mbaro r…®ghe
\r (Mat 21:23-27; Luk 20:1-8)
\p 
\v 27 Jisas na gharaghambu vambowo veth…® vuthava Jerusalem. MbaŇča i loŇčgaloŇčga e Ňägolo Bobomako ghayayao t…®ne, ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye, mbaro gharavavaghare na giyagiya vavanava th…® rakamenawe,
\v 28 na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU vata thela ele mbaro vwatae iya u vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake? Thela i dage e ghen na u vakathaŇčgi?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo ya vaitoŇčga vaito regha na thoŇčgo hu wogiya ghathombe e ghino, amba ya utuŇča weŇčga ya vata thela e vwatae na ya vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake.
\v 30 Jon le r…®ghe i bap…®taiso, i mena weya Loi o i mena weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Mbe thiye eŇčge th…® veutu weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo raŇča, ‚ÄėI mena weya Loi‚Äô, ne iŇča, ‚ÄėBuda kaiwae mava hu loŇčweghath…®gha Jon?‚Äô
\v 32 Ko thoŇčgo raŇča, ‚ÄėI mena weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®‚ÄĒ‚Äô‚ÄĚ (Va th…® mararuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® loŇčweghath…® emunjoru Jon iye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu.)
\v 33 Iya kaiwae th…® gonjogha weya Jisas th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa wo ghareghare.‚ÄĚ
\p Iya kaiwae Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ma ne ya utuveŇčga, ya vata thela e vwatae na ya vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake.‚ÄĚ
\c 12
\s1 Uma gharanjimbunjimbu raraithar…®
\r (Mat 21:33-46; Luk 20:9-19)
\p 
\v 1 Amba Jisas i utu weŇčgi e goghaimba iŇča, ‚ÄúLolo regha va i kabu waen ghauma, i gana vagh…®liya, i vakatha doda waen ghamba i imb…®imb…®, na i vatada Ňčgolo regha, umako gharanjimbunjimbu lenji ghamba yaku. I vakatha Ňčgoreiyako, amba i vatomwe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana na th…® vakaiwoŇča amalagh…®niye kaiwae. Amba amalagh…®niye i wa ve gh…®nagha e vanautuma regha.
\v 2 MbaŇča kaero ghambaŇča th…® vu, umako tanuwagae i variya le rakakaiwo regha weŇčgiya gharanjimbunjimbuko na ve bigiya uneune vavana weŇčgi amalagh…®niye kaiwae.
\v 3 Ranjimbunjimbuko th…® yalaweya rakakaiwoko, th…® tagavotagamenawe na th…® variye njogha n…®man…®ma.
\v 4 Mbowo i variyeva le rakakaiwo regha, ranjimbunjimbuko th…® Ňčge e umbaliye na th…® vakatha ghamba monjina moliwe.
\v 5 Umako tanuwagae mbowo i variyeva le rakakaiwo regha ko iyemaeŇčge th…® tagavamare. Va th…® vakatha weŇčgiya vavana tembe Ňčgorava iyako, vavana th…® ŇčgeŇčgeŇčaŇčgi na vavana th…® tagavavamareŇčgi.
\v 6 Vama reghaeŇčge vara moli mbe inawe, nariye na val…®ghareghare moli. Muyai moli amba i variye weŇčgiya umako gharanjimbunjimbu na iŇča, ‚ÄėYa ghareghare ne th…® yavwatatawana naruŇčguke.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúKo iyemaeŇčge umako gharanjimbunjimbu th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėUmake tanuwagae nariye maiya i menake. Iye ne i rombaroŇča umake ramae e ghereiye. Hu rakamena ra tagavamare na mbalama ra mbaroŇčava iya le umake!‚Äô
\v 8 Amba th…® yalawe na th…® tagavamare, na th…® wokiyathuraŇčgiya e gana ghereiye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Jisas i govaito iŇča, ‚ÄúUmako tanuwagae ne i vakatha budakai? Ne i mena i gaboŇčgi na ma i vatomweva umako weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana.
\v 10 Vambe hu vaona Buk Boboma le utu Mesaiya kaiwae, iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėVar…®ke iya Ňčgoloke gharavatavatad th…® botewo, kaero i tabo na ghambagh…®mbagh…®.
\v 11 Iyake Giya n…®mae muiye na ghayamoyamo i thovuye moli e maranda.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 12:11 \xt Sam 118:22-23\x* Jisas i utu Ňčgoreiyake na utuke thiyake i vatomwe thavala th…® botewo Loi nariye.
\p 
\v 12 Amba Jiu lenji randeviva nuwanjiya th…® yalawe kaiwae va th…® ghareghare goghaimbako iyako thiye ghanjigoghaimba. Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® mararuŇčgiya wabwiko lagh…®ye, iya kaiwae th…® roitete na th…® rakawa.
\s1 Vaito takis kaiwae
\r (Mat 22:15-22; Luk 20:20-26)
\p 
\v 13 Amba th…® variyeŇčgiya Parisi vavana na Herod le wabwi ghar…®ghar…®niye vavana weya Jisas th…® munje th…® vaito na th…® vakatha ghawonjowe ele utuutuko.
\v 14 MbaŇča th…® menawe kaero th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, wo ghareghare u utuŇča emunjoru na ma u goru weya ŇčgoroŇčga ghar…®ghar…® lenji renuwaŇča. Ma u goruwe ŇčgoroŇčga lolo le thimba o le lagh…®lagh…®ye, ko emunjoru u vavaghareŇča Loi le renuwaŇča ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji. U utugiya weime, ŇčgoroŇčga, la mbaro i vatomwe weime na wo vamodo takis weya Sisa, o nandere?
\v 15 Wo vamodo o thava wo vamodo?‚ÄĚ
\p Ko Jisas kaero i thuwe lenji kwan…®ko na i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae hu munje hu mandoŇčgo? Wo hu woma manina geth…®ra na ya thuwe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Th…® womena geth…®rawe na i vatomwe weŇčgi, i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThela ŇčgaliŇčgaliya na idayake?‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúSisa.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúSisa le bigibigi hu wogiya weya Sisa na Loi le bigibigi hu wogiya weya Loi.‚ÄĚ\fig Sisa ŇčgaliŇčgaliyae ina Rom lenji mani|alt="coins with Caesar pictures" src="hk00166c.tif" size="col" copy="BFBS (Knowles)" ref="12:13-17"\fig*
\p Na Jisas le utuko i wo nuwanji.
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare thuweiruva utuniye
\r (Mat 22:22-33; Luk 20:27-40)
\p 
\v 18 Amba Sadusi, thiye ma th…® loŇčweghath…® ramaremare tembene th…® thuweiruva, vavana th…® rakawa weya Jisas na th…® vaito th…®Ňča,
\v 19 ‚ÄúRavavaghare, Mosese va i roriya mbaroke iyake kaiwanda, iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo amala i mare iteta levo ko ma i ghamb…® weiye, ghaghae ma i rovaŇčguva gh…®mbwiyeko. ThoŇčgo i ghamb…® weiye, gamagaiko thiyako ghaghaeko va i mareko le ŇčgaŇčga.‚Äô\x - \xo 12:19 \xt Mba 25:5\x*
\v 20 MbaŇča regha amala regha na oghaghae; va theghepir…® vara, t…®nanji na ramanji regha. Lagh…®yeninji va i ghe na amba ma th…® ghamb…® weiye kaero i mare itetava levo.
\v 21 Ghaghae theghewoniye i rovaŇčgu na tembe ma i ghamb…®va weiye kaero i mare. Theghetoninji vambe Ňčgoreiyeva, kamwath…®ko iyako te vambe i yomaraweva.
\v 22 Vambe Ňčgoreiye varako taulagh…®ko weŇčgi. Theghepir…®ko va th…® vaŇčgwa elako na thiya marevao ma th…® ghamb…® weinji. Va ele ghambako elagh…®niye i mare.
\v 23 Ko mbaŇča ne ramaremare th…® thuweiru na e yawayawalinjiva, thela ne i ghe weiye, kaiwae vambe theghepir…®ko vara th…® vaŇčgu?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero hu vur…®thavwiya kamwath…®, kaiwae ma hu ghareghare Buk Boboma le woraŇčgiya ŇčgoroŇčga gharumwaru na budakaiya Loi val…®kaiwae i vakatha.
\v 25 Kaiwae mbaŇča ramaremare ne th…® thuweiru na tembe e yawayawalinjiva, ma tembene th…® gheva, thiye ne Ňčgoranjiya nyao thovuthovuye e buruburu.
\v 26 Iya ramaremare tembene th…® thuweiruva kaiwanji: mbe hu ndevaona mun Mosese le rorori, utuutuma iyava nd…®ghema i ra e umbwaumbwama ndamwandamwa utuniye? Eibraham, Aisake, na Jeikob vama th…® mare na mbaŇča molao e ghereiye amba Loi i dage weya Mosese, iŇča ‚ÄėGhino Eibraham le Loi, Aisake le Loi, na Jeikob le Loi.‚Äô\x - \xo 12:26 \xt RaŇč 3:6,15\x*
\v 27 Iye ma ramaremare lenji Loi, nandere. Iye ghar…®ghar…® e yawayawalinji lenji Loi. Ghemi hu kwan, hu vur…®thavwi moli.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mbaro lagh…®ye moli
\r (Mat 22:34-40; Luk 10:25-28)
\p 
\v 28 Mbaro gharavavaghare reghava ina gheko, i vandeŇče e lenji utuko. I thuweya Jisas le thombe weŇčgiya Sadusiko i thovuye, i mena i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThe mbaro i lagh…®ye vara moli?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaro lagh…®ye moli iyake: ‚ÄėHu vandeŇče, ghemi wabwi Isirel! Giya la Loi, ghamberegha moli iye Giya.
\v 30 Hu gharethovu Giya lemi Loi, e gharemina lagh…®ye, e unemina lagh…®ye, e lemi renuwaŇčana lagh…®ye, na e lemi vur…®gheghena lagh…®ye.‚Äô\x - \xo 12:30 \xt Mba 6:4-5\x*
\v 31 Mbaro lagh…®ye moli theghewoniye iyake: U gharethovu weya ghanu Ňčgoreiya u gharethovu e ghen.\x - \xo 12:31 \xt Liv 19:18\x* Ma te mbaro reghava i lagh…®ye kivwala iya theghewoke thiyake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Mbaroko gharavavaghare i dage weya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúI thovuye moli, Ravavaghare! Emunjoru Ňčgoreiya moŇčana Giya iye Loi mbe ghamberegha eŇčge na ma te Loi reghava, ghamberegha moli.
\v 33 Na ra gharethovu Loi e gharendake lagh…®ye na e la renuwaŇčake lagh…®ye na e la vur…®ghegheke lagh…®ye. Thiyake th…® lagh…®ye kivwala ra wogiya thetheghan mbwanambwana moli e ghamba vowo na vowo vavanava weva Loi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 Jisas i thuweya le thombeko th…® thovuye moli na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMa inan bwagabwaga Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p Iyake e ghereiye taulagh…®ko ma te th…® vaitova Jisas kaiwae th…® ghareghare ma val…®kaiwae th…® kwan…®yaro.
\s1 Vaito Mesaiya kaiwae
\r (Mat 22:41-46; Luk 20:41-44)
\p 
\v 35 MbaŇča Jisas i vavaghare e Ňägolo Boboma ghayayao t…®ne amba i vaitoŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga na iya mbaroko gharavavaghare th…®Ňča Mesaiya iye Deivid rumbuye?
\v 36 MbaŇča me vivako Nyao Boboma i vakatha Deivid iyava iŇčake, ‚ÄėGiya Loi i dage weya wo Giya iŇča: ‚ÄúU yaku val…®vaŇčga e uneŇčguke ghaghad ya biginjoŇčaŇčgiya ghan…®th…®gh…®ya e gheghen raberabe.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 12:36 \xt Sam 110:1\x*
\p 
\v 37 ‚ÄúDeivid ghamberegha i una Mesaiya ‚ÄėGiya‚Äô. ŇägoroŇčga eŇčge na iye Deivid rumbuye?‚ÄĚ Na wabwiko lagh…®ye th…® vandeŇče weinji lenji warari.
\s1 Jisas i utuŇča mbaro gharavavaghare kaiwanji
\r (Mat 23:1-36; Luk 20:45-47)
\p 
\v 38 Na Jisas ele vavaghare t…®ne iŇča, ‚ÄúHu njimbukikiŇčga weŇčgiya mbaro gharavavaghare. Thiye nuwanjiya th…® njimbo ghanjikwama molamolao na th…® ndeloŇčga na thoŇčgo th…® lavolevoleŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® nuwanjiya weiye lenji yavwatata th…® dage mwaewo weŇčgi.
\v 39 Jiu e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne, thiye nuwanjiya th…® roviva ghar…®ghar…® e ghamwanji, na thaga e t…®ne nuwanjiya veth…® yaku Ňčgora ghar…®ghar…® lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghamba yaku.
\v 40 Th…® yabo wambwiwambwi maranji na th…® mbaroŇčaŇčgiya lenji ŇčgoloŇčgolo na lenji bigibigi, na kaiwae nuwanjiya th…® yabo lenji vakathaŇčgiko th…® vakatha naŇčgo molamolao ghar…®ghar…® e maranji. Ko iyemaeŇčge lenji vakathako kaiwae ne th…® vaidiya vuyowo lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ E utuutuke thiyake Jisas i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčgi mbaro gharavavaghare kaiwanji.
\s1 Wambwi le mwaewo
\r (Luk 21:1-4)
\p 
\v 41 E Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne Jisas i yaku e mani ghamba bigirawe ghadidiye na i njimbukikiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® bigibigirawa mani. Ghar…®ghar…® lenji bigibigi i ghanagha th…® bigiraweya mani i ghanagha.
\v 42 Amba wambwi eunda, mbinyembinyeŇčgu, i mena na i bigiraweya toeya gethiwo rere.
\v 43 I kula vathaŇčgiya gharaghambu na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, wambwiko iya mbinyembinyeŇčguko me bigiraweko i lagh…®ye kivwala vara iya taulagh…®ko meth…® bigirawe.
\v 44 Kaiwae vavana meth…® bigiraweya mani vavana na lagh…®yeniye mbe inawe, ko elagh…®niye, kaiwae iye mbinyembinyeŇčgu, le manima wolagh…®ye ghae modae maiyavara me bigirawe vunuko.‚ÄĚ
\c 13
\s1 Jisas iŇča Ňägolo Boboma ne i marakaraka
\r (Mat 24:1-2; Luk 21:5-6)
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča Jisas i raŇčgima e Ňägolo Bobomako ghayayao t…®ne gharaghambu regha i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, wo u thuweŇčgiya ŇčgoloŇčgoloke lagh…®lagh…®ye na var…®var…®ke lagh…®lagh…®ye va th…® vatadakowe! Mbema ghanjiyamoyamo i thovuye vara moli.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 2 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúIya u thuweŇčgiya ŇčgoloŇčgoloko lagh…®lagh…®ye thiyako, mavole var…® regha i ndeghath…® ele ghamba ndeghath…®. Wolagh…®yeko nevole th…® bigiyathuvao na iko.‚ÄĚ
\s1 MbaŇča le ghambako ghanono
\r (Luk 21:7-19)
\p 
\v 3 MbaŇča Jisas ve yaku Oliv…® e ghanji Ou, e Ňägolo Boboma na val…®mbwa amba Pita, Jemes, Jon na Endru, mbe thiye eŇčge, th…® vaito thuwele th…®Ňča,
\v 4 ‚ÄúU utugiya weime, thembaŇča vara na bigibigiko mo utuŇčaŇčgiko ne th…® yomara? Na ghanjinono ne ŇčgoroŇčga i ghaŇčgo?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčga, tha lolo regha i yaroŇčga.
\v 6 Kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® i ghanagha ne th…® mena e idaŇčgu na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėGhino Mesaiya!‚Äô na ne th…® yaroŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo.
\v 7 Nono reghava iyake. Ne hu loŇčweŇčgiya vanautuma lenji gaith…® utuniye na toto gaith…® kaiwae, ko hu ndemararu. Bigibigike Ňčgoranjiyake ne th…® yomara, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča le ghambako amba mane i mena.
\v 8 Vanautuma ne th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi; rambarombaro ne th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi. Nevole vunuvu na ragheragheghe lemoyo e yambaneke lagh…®ye. Vuyowoke thiyake ne th…® yomara Ňčgoreiya Ňčgama i vwara ghatambwa na v…®r…®niye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúGhemi tembe ghamimberegha hu njimbukiki. Ne th…® yalaweŇčga na th…® vaŇčguŇčga na vohu kot. Ne veth…® gaboŇčga e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne; ne th…® vakatha na hu ndeghath…® rambarombaro na kiŇč e ghamwanji idaŇčgu kaiwae na hu utuŇča weŇčgiya Toto Thovuye.
\v 10 Ko amba muyai yambaneke le ghambako wone lo ghar…®ghar…® th…® utuŇča Toto Thovuye e yambaneke lagh…®ye.
\v 11 Na mbaŇča ne th…® yalaweŇčga na th…® yovaŇčguŇčga kot kaiwae, gharemi ne i ndegaith…® lemi utu kaiwae amba muyai kot ghambaŇča. MbaŇča ne ghamimbaŇča utu, hu utuŇčaŇčgiya thedage iya ne i yomara e nuwamina. Kaiwae dageŇčgina ne hu utuŇčaŇčgina ma ghan…®mbereghana ghal…®Ňčami; ne th…® mena weya Nyao Boboma.
\v 12 Amaamala vavana ne th…® vatomweŇčgiya oghaghanji na th…® gaboŇčgi, na gamagai oramanjiŇčgi ne th…® vakatha weŇčgiya lenji ŇčgaŇčga Ňčgoreiye. Gamagai vavana ne th…® ndeghereiye wanaŇčgiya otatanji na oramanji na th…® vakathaŇčgi na th…® gaboŇčgi.
\v 13 Ghino kaiwaŇčgu taulagh…® ne th…® botewoyathuŇčga. Ko the lolo i ghataŇčaghath…® ghaghada ne le ghambako Loi i vamora yawaliye.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Bigiko i ndeghath…® Ňčgoreiye ma val…®kaiwae i ndeghath…®we
\r (Mat 24:15-28; Luk 21:20-24)
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne hu thuweya bigiko i vamb…®gh…®ya Ňägolo Boboma na i vakatha ghar…®ghar…® th…® roitetako,\f + \fr 13:14 \ft Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu Daniyel va i utuutu loi vatavatad le ghamba vowo Antiyokas Epipeins ne i vatad e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne Jerusalem ‚ÄĒ e theghathegha 168 B.C. Grik lenji loi lagh…®ye idae Jeus, va th…® kururuwe (Dan 9:27; 11:31 na 12:11). Iyake Jisas va i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčgi ne e kamwath…®ke iyake ghar…®ghar…® th…® vamb…®gh…®ya Ňägolo Bobomako. Buk Boboma gharaghareghare th…® renuwaŇča govambwarako iyako va i yomara mbaŇča Rom th…® rakamena th…® tagarakaraka Jerusalem weiye Ňägolo Boboma, theghathegha A.D. 70 e t…®ne. IyemaeŇčge vavana th…® renuwaŇča i utuutu Krais ghath…®gh…®ya kaiwae (2Tes 2:3-10; 1Jon 2:18,20), amba i menamenako, na vavana tembe th…®Ňčava i utuuta Jilot kaiwanji (Mak 3:18), iya th…® vamb…®gh…®ya Ňägolo Bobomako ‚ÄĒ theghathegha A.D. 67-68. Kaiwae govambwara regha na regha mbaŇčaviye iya lenji yomara ‚ÄĒ val…®kaiwae i vamboromboro iya ma utuŇčaŇčgiko na vavanava, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva amba muyai yambaneke le ghambako (Ňčgoreiye r…®ghethoru 24-25 lenji govambwara).\f* na i ndeghath…® Ňčgoreiye ma val…®kaiwae i ndeghath…®we.‚ÄĚ (Ghemi buk iyake gharavavaona wo hu rerenuwaŇča ghaghad…® nuwamina i rumwaruŇča utuke iyake!) ‚ÄúMbaŇčaniye thavala inanji Judiya th…® vo weya e ououko r…®ghenji.
\v 15 ThoŇčgo lolo regha ina ele Ňčgolo vwatae ne i nderu ele Ňčgolo t…®ne, i wo le bigi regha na i yowo weiye.
\v 16 Lolo regha ina e uma t…®ne ne i ndenjogha ele Ňčgolo na i liya ghakwama ghayaboyabo.
\v 17 Ne e mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako ne i vuyowo lagh…®ye moli weŇčgiya wanakau thiya marabo na wanakau weinjiyaŇčgiya gamagai amba th…® thuthu.
\v 18 Hu naŇčgo weya Loi na bigibigike thiyake ne th…® ndeyomara mbaŇča njigh…®njigh…® ghambaŇča.
\v 19 Vuyowo ne e mbaŇčako iyako ne i lagh…®ye, i lagh…®ye moli. Na vuyowoko Ňčgoranjiyako ma mbaŇča regha i yomara e yambaneke va i rikowe gheghada noroke, na ma tene Ňčgoreiyeva mbaŇča muyai.
\v 20 ThoŇčgo ma Loi i wonjaniya mbaŇča le molamolao, mbala ma lolo regha i moru. Ko le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwae, Loi kaero i wonjoŇča vuyowo ghambaŇča le molamolao.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo lolo regha i dage e ghen, ‚ÄėWo u thuwe, Mesaiya maiya!‚Äô o ‚ÄėWo u thuwe, maiyako!‚Äô, ne u ndeloŇčweghath…®.
\v 22 Kaiwae Mesaiya kwan…®kwan na Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan ne th…® rakaraŇčgi. Ne th…® vakathaŇčgiya vakatha ghamba rotaele, na th…® wo ghar…®ghar…® nuwanji na th…® munje tembe th…® wova Loi le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye nuwanji.
\v 23 Hu njimbukikiŇčga! Kaero ma utuveŇčga bigibigike wolagh…®ye amba muyai th…® yomara.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Lolo Nariye le yomara
\r (Mat 24:29-31; Luk 21:25-28)
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúKo iyemaeŇčge ne e mbaŇčako thiyako, vuyowoko e ghereiye varae mara ne i momouwo, manjala mane i mb…®le,
\v 25 gh…®tara ne th…® dobu na buruburu matemate ne th…® nyiv…®vao.
\v 26 Amba Lolo Nariye i yomara na th…® thuwe. Ne i njama e Ňčgal…®l…®ko weiye vur…®gheghe lagh…®ye na vwenyevwenye.\x - \xo 13:26 \xt Dan 7:13\x*
\v 27 Ne i variyeŇčgiya le nyao thovuthovuye e yambaneke ghadidiye geth…®var…® na th…® vaŇčguvathavathaŇčgiya le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye e yambaneke mbothiye regha gheghada val…®mbothiye.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Vavaghare i mena e umbwa fig
\r (Mat 24:32-35; Luk 21:29-33)
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúUmbwa fig i woveŇčga goghaimba thovuye. MbaŇča yaŇčgayaŇčga amba ma th…® vur…®gheghe na ndamwandamwa togha th…® thalavwara u ghareghareya thuwai ghambaŇča kaero ma bwagabwaga.
\v 29 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, mbaŇča ne hu thuweŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake th…® yoyomara ne hu ghareghare le njoghama ghambaŇča kaero ma bwagabwaga, maiyavara.
\v 30 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, thake iyake mamba ne thiya marevao ghaghad bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake th…® yomara.
\v 31 Buruburu na yambane ne th…®ko, ko ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke mane iko.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Ma lolo regha i ghareghare thembaŇča na thelughawoghawo
\r (Mat 24:36-44)
\p 
\v 32 ‚ÄúKo iyemaeŇčge ma lolo regha i ghareghare thembaŇča o the lughawoghawo vara Lolo Nariye ne i menawe. Buruburu nyaoniye thovuthovuye ma th…® ghareghare na mbe Ňčgoreiyeva Loi Nariye; ko mbe Ramae ghamberegha eŇčge i ghareghare ne thembaŇča.
\v 33 Hu njimbukikiŇčga na hu njaŇčanjaŇča, kaiwae ma hu ghareghare thembaŇča ne i menawe.
\v 34 Ne Ňčgoreiya lolo regha i iteta le Ňčgolo na i wa ve gh…®nagha. I bigiraweŇčgiya le rakakaiwo na th…® njimbukiki. Regha na regha mbe ghakaiwo amba i dage weya th…®n…®mba gharanjimbunjimbu na i njaŇčanjaŇča le njoghama kaiwae.
\v 35 Iya kaiwae hu njaŇčanja, kaiwae ma hu ghareghare thembaŇča Ňčgolo tanuwaga, ne i vutha ‚ÄĒ ne yegh…®yegh…®yenja, o gougou mborowa, o kamkam i dagedage, o varae i maremuyagh…®.
\v 36 ThoŇčgo i vutha vararaŇčga, ne i ndevaidiŇčga hu ghenelaŇča.
\v 37 Budakaiya ya utuveŇčga tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ya utuveŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye: Hu njaŇčanjaŇča!‚ÄĚ
\c 14
\s1 Jiu lenji randeviva th…® vona Jisas ghae
\r (Mat 26:1-5; Luk 22:1-2; Jon 11:45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Vama mbaŇča theghewo eŇčge kaero Thaga ValaŇčani na Bred ma weiye is…®t ghanjithaga. Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare th…® vona Jisas ghae na nuwanjiya th…® yalawe thuwele na th…® un…®gh…®.
\v 2 Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa val…®kaiwae ra vakatha e thagake t…®ne ne iwaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® gharenji i muru na th…® gaith…®.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Wevo eunda i varuvu Jisas e bunama
\r (Mat 26:6-13; Jon 12:1-8)
\p 
\v 3 Jisas ina Betani Saimon ele Ňčgolo. Amalake iyake va i ghataŇča lepelo. MbaŇča Jisas i ghan…®Ňčga weiyaŇčgi wevo eunda i menawe, i th…®na bod…®la alabasita vwarara bunama inawe. Bunamake iyake idae nad na modae lagh…®ye moli. I mwanabeba bod…®lako numwe kaero i liŇčgiya bunamako Jisas e umbaliye.
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® va inanji gheko, vavana weinji lenji ghatemuru th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga ghathovuye bunama modae lagh…®ye i kaiwo Ňčgorako?
\v 5 Bunamake mbalava i vakuneŇča na val…®kaiwae modae i lareŇčawe theghathegha umbwara modae na i giya weŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu.‚ÄĚ Mbema th…® vethowana vara lagh…®ye moli.
\p 
\v 6 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu viyathu! Tembe ghamberegha! Buda kaiwae hu liya ghautu? Me vakatha bigi thovuye e ghino.
\v 7 Kaiwae mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ne weimiyaŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu, na thembaŇča nuwamina nuwaiya val…®kaiwae hu thalavuŇčgi. Ko iyemaeŇčge mane weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi gheke mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye.
\v 8 Kaiwae me vakatha budakaiya me val…®kaiwae, kaero me varuvuŇčgo amba muyai ne mbaŇča i mena beku kaiwae.
\v 9 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, aŇčgavole th…® vavaghareŇča Toto Thovuye e yambaneke lagh…®ye, budakaiya wevoke iyake me vakatha ghar…®ghar…® ne th…® utuŇča na th…® renuwaŇčakikiya elagh…®niye.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® dagerawe Judas modae
\r (Mat 26:14-16; Luk 22:3-6)
\p 
\v 10 Amba Judas Isakariyot, gharaghambuko theyaworo na theghewoko regha, i wa weŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye kaiwae nuwaiya i vatomweya Jisas weŇčgi.
\v 11 Na mbaŇča th…® loŇčweya iyako nuwanji i loghe na th…® dagerawa modae. Amba i tamweya kamwath…® thovuye na i vatomwe weŇčgi.
\s1 Jisas na gharaghambu th…® vakatha Thaga ValaŇčani
\r (Mat 26:17-25; Luk 22:7-14,21-23; Jon 13:21-30)
\p 
\v 12 MbaŇča iviva moli Bred ma weiye is…®t ghathaga ghambaŇča, mbaŇčaniye th…® gaboŇčgiya sip nariye Thaga ValaŇčani ghan…®Ňčganiye kaiwae, gharaghambu th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNuwaniya aŇčga wo wa na vo vivatha Thaga ValaŇčani ghan…®Ňčganiye kaiwan?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Jisas i variyeŇčgiya gharaghambu theghewo iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa vohu ru e ghembana t…®ne, na amala i th…®na mbwa e mbwa variye ne i lavolevoleŇčga. Hu mbele,
\v 14 na the Ňčgolo ve ruwe, hu dage weya Ňčgolona tanuwagae huŇča, ‚ÄėRavavaghare i vaito: IyaŇčganiya woluwolu bobwari kaiwaŇčgu na ne ya ghana Thaga ValaŇčani ghan…®Ňčganiye weiŇčguyaŇčgiya woraghambuke?‚Äô
\v 15 Na ne i vatomwe weŇčga woluwolu lagh…®ye ina yavoro na ghan…®Ňčga bigibiginiye kaero inanjiwe; ghena hu vakatharawa ghan…®Ňčganawe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Gharaghambuko th…® wa na veth…® ru e ghembako t…®ne, na veth…® vaidi Ňčgoreiya me dagema weŇčgi; na th…® vivatharaweya Thaga ValaŇčani ghan…®Ňčganiyewe.
\p 
\v 17 Vama gougou e mbaŇčako iyako Jisas i mena weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambuko theyaworo na theghewo.
\v 18 Ghan…®Ňčga e t…®ne Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, regha ghemi iya ya ghan…®Ňčgake weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi, ne i vatomweŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Gharenji i v…®r…® lagh…®ye na th…® dagewe, regha na regha iya i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, ma ghino Ňčgoreiye, ae?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemina iya themiyaworo na themighewona regha, iya i wouta ghabred…®na weiŇčgu e gaeba regha.
\v 21 Lolo Nariye ne i mare Ňčgoreiya Buk Boboma le woraŇčgiya, ko iyemaeŇčge loloko iya ne i vatomweya Lolo Nariye ne i vaidiya vuyowae. I thovuye moliwa loloko iyako thoŇčgo t…®nae ma va i ghamb…® eŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare dagerawe togha kaiwae
\r (Mat 26:26-30; Luk 22:14-20; 1Kor 11:23-25)
\p 
\v 22 MbaŇča thiya ghan…®Ňčga, Jisas i wo bred mbumbura, i vata ago weya Loi, i mwanaviya na i giya weŇčgiya gharaghambuko, na iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wo na hu ghan. Iyake riwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Na i th…®na kom na tembe i vata ago weva Loi, i th…®n…®giya weŇčgi na thiya mun.
\v 24 Amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWaen…®ke iyake mad…®baŇčgu, iye i vaemunjoruŇča dagerawe togha. I voruraŇčgi ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo kaiwanji.
\v 25 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, ma tene ya mun…®va waen…®ke iyake ghaghada ne ya mun…®va waen togha Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 MbaŇča th…® wothuvao wothu yaŇčgara th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® raka Oliv…® e ghanji Ou.
\s1 Jisas i dage weya Pita iŇča, ‚ÄúNe uŇča, ‚ÄėYa roro Jisas.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\r (Mat 26:31-35; Luk 22:31-34; Jon 13:36-38)
\p 
\v 27 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTaulagh…®na ghemi ne hu iteteŇčgo, kaiwae Buk Boboma iŇča, ‚ÄėNe ya un…®gha sip ghanjiranjimbunjimbu na sip th…® rakavo.‚Äô\x - \xo 14:27 \xt Sak 3:7\x*
\v 28 Ko amba Loi ne i vakathaŇčgo na ya thuweiru, na ya viva e ghamwami Galili.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Pita i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúOthembe taulagh…®ke ne th…® rakavo, ghino ma Ňčgoreiye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Jisas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghen, amba muyai kamkam i dage mbaŇčaiwo noroke gougou, mbaŇčato ne uŇča ma u ghareghareŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Pita i gonjoghawe weiye ghal…®Ňčae vur…®gheghe iŇča, ‚ÄúMane yaŇča ma ya ghareghareŇčge, othembe thoŇčgo ya mare weiŇčgu ghen.‚ÄĚ Na taulagh…®ko th…® utuŇča Ňčgoreiye.
\s1 Jisas i naŇčgo Getesemani
\r (Mat 26:36-46; Luk 22:39-46)
\p 
\v 32 MbaŇča Jisas na gharaghambu th…® mena e Oliv…® ghauma idae Getesemani, i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHuya yaku gheke, na wo va naŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\v 33 I vaŇčguŇčgiya Pita, Jemes na Jon weiyaŇčgi. Jisas ghare i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli.
\v 34 Amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhareŇčguke i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli, mbalama i tagavamareŇčgo. Hu yaku gheke na hu njaŇčanjaŇča.‚ÄĚ\fig Jisas i naŇčgo weya Ramae Getesemani e t…®ne|alt="Jesus in Gethsemane" src="IB04155bw.tif" size="col" copy="Faadil" ref="14:32-42"\fig*
\p 
\v 35 I loŇčga ghaova seiwo, i dipoumu e thelauko vwatae na i naŇčgo thoŇčgo val…®kaiwae thava i ru vuyowoko iyako e t…®ne.
\v 36 IŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe, Bwebwe! Bigibigike wolagh…®ye val…®kaiwan. ThoŇčgo nuwaniya, u th…®na vuyowoke ghandegh…® e ghino. Ko iyemaeŇčge thava u vakatha ghino lo renuwaŇča, u vakathaeŇčge ghen len renuwaŇča.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 37 I njoghama na i vaidiŇčgi thiya ghena, na i dage weya Pita iŇča, ‚ÄúSaimon, ko hu ghenelaŇčava? Ma val…®kaiwae hu yaku na hu njaŇčanjaŇča lughawoghawo regha?‚ÄĚ
\v 38 Amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu njaŇčanjaŇča na hu naŇčgo, mbala ma hu ru tanathetha e t…®ne. Ghare nuwaiya, ko ririwo i njavovo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 39 Jisas i wa na mbowo ve naŇčgova na i naŇčgo na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva me naŇčgokaima.
\v 40 Na mbowo i njoghama weŇčgiva gharaghambuma i vaidi tembe th…® ghenelaŇčava kaiwae mara ghenaghena i gaboŇčgi. Na ma th…® ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga th…®Ňčawe.
\p 
\v 41 MbaŇča i njoghamava mbaŇčatoninji, i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKo amba hu ghenaghena vara mbaŇčake molao? Thama ghanjighena! MbaŇča kaero iko; e mbaŇčake vara th…® vaŇčguraweya Lolo Nariye thar…® gharavakatha e n…®manji ghare.
\v 42 Hu yondo na ra raka. Wo hu thuwe, loloma wolilivama maiyavara i menana!‚ÄĚ
\s1 Th…® yalaweya Jisas
\r (Mat 26:47-56; Luk 22:47-53; Jon 18:3-12)
\p 
\v 43 Jisas vamba i utuutu kaero Judas, gharaghambuma theyaworo na theghewoma regha, i vutha weiyaŇčgiya wabwi lagh…®ye regha. Th…® mban…®Ňčgiya gaith…® ghaghalith…® na umbwaumbwa uboubotu. Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye, mbaro gharavavaghare na giyagiya vavanava meth…® variyeŇčgi.
\v 44 Lilivama vama i giya nono weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThe lolo ne ya vandamo, ee amalagh…®niye. Hu yalawe na mbe weimi vara hu yovaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 45 MbaŇča Judas i vutha, i mwand…®we Jisas na iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare!‚ÄĚ Na i vandamo.
\v 46 Iya kaiwae th…® yalawe e n…®manji na th…® vikiki.
\v 47 Ko ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® ndeghath…®ko regha i mwanagita le gaith…® ghaghalith…® e ghambae na i gothethe ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva le rakakaiwo yanawae.
\v 48 Jisas i dage weŇčgiya wabwima iŇča, ‚ÄúMohuŇča eŇčge rakaiva ghino iya mohu mban…®Ňčgiya gaith…®na ghaghalith…® na umbwaumbwa uboubotu na hu mena hu yalaweŇčgo?
\v 49 MbaŇča regha na regha weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi ya vavaghare e Ňägolo Boboma na mava hu yalaweŇčgo. Ko iyemaeŇčge iyake i vaemunjoruŇča Buk Boboma.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 50 Amba gharaghambuko th…® voiteteŇča.
\v 51 Amala regha, amba tabwagha, vambe i njimbo eŇčge kwama yaŇčgara. I rereghamba weya Jisas. Wabwiko th…® munje th…® yalawe,
\v 52 ko i vo bukabuka, na i iteta ghakwama e ghereiye.
\s1 Jisas i utu Jiu e lenji kot lagh…®ye
\r (Mat 26:57-68; Luk 22:66-71; Jon 18:13-14,19-24)
\p 
\v 53 Th…® yovaŇčguya Jisas ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva ele Ňčgolo Ňčgora vama ravowovowo, giyagiya na mbaro gharavavaghare inanjiwe.
\v 54 Na Pita i rereghamba, vambe ina bwagabwaga na ve ru ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva le Ňčgolo e ghayayao. I ru na i yaku weiyaŇčgiya rakakaiwo na i mwa nd…®ghe.
\v 55 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na rambarombaro Jiu e lenji kot lagh…®ye\f + \fr 14:55 \ft Jiu lenji kot lagh…®ye idae Sanhidren.\f* t…®ne th…® mando na th…® tamweya ghar…®ghar…® val…®kaiwanji th…® utu kaiwae na i mare, ko ma th…® ndevaidi mun.
\v 56 Th…® ghanagha th…® utu kwan…®kwan kaiwae, ko lenji utuko ma mboromboro.
\v 57 Amba vavana th…® yondo na th…® utuŇča kwan…®ke iyake kaiwae th…®Ňča,
\v 58 ‚ÄúVa wo loŇčweya iŇča, ‚ÄėNe ya raka Ňägolo Bobomake iyava ghar…®ghar…®ke th…® vatad na mbaŇča thegheto e t…®ne kaero ya vatad…®va regha ma ghar…®ghar…® th…® vatad e n…®manji!‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\v 59 Ko iyemaeŇčge lenji utuko ma mboromboro.
\v 60 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva i yondo e maranji na i dage weya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúKo mane u gonjogha lenji utuko ghath…®th…®? ŇägoroŇčga lenji utuko gharumwaru e ghen?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 61 Ko Jisas mava i ndegolambo mun. Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva mbowo i vaitova iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Mesaiya, iya taulagh…®ke ra yavwatatawanake Nariye?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 62 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, na ne hu thuwe Lolo Nariye i yaku Loi Vur…®gheghe e uneko na i njama e Ňčgal…®l…®Ňčgiko e buruburu.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 14:62 \xt Sam 110:1; Dan 7:13\x*
\p 
\v 63 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva i mwanathethe ghakwama ghatemuru kaiwae na iŇča, ‚ÄúMa te nuwandaiyava ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® utu kaiwae. Kaero mohu loŇčweya le utuko, me utuvathar…® weya Loi.
\v 64 ŇägoroŇčga lemi renuwaŇča?‚ÄĚ Taulagh…®ko th…®Ňča: ‚ÄúVal…®kaiwae moliya i mare!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 65 Amba vavana th…® njoŇčgovun na th…® Ňčgar…®gana marae na th…® Ňčge e n…®manji na th…® vatabweyaruŇča th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ghal…®Ňčae gharautu ghen, u dage weime thela me ŇčgeŇčgena.‚ÄĚ Ragagaith…® th…® vaŇčgu na th…® levalevaŇča.
\s1 Pita iŇča ma i ghareghare Jisas
\r (Mat 26:69-75; Luk 22:54-62; Jon 18:15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 66 Pita vambe ina bode e Ňčgoloko ghayayao amba ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva le rakakaiwo eunda i mena Ňčgora Pita inamawe.
\v 67 MbaŇča i thuwe Pita i mwamwa nd…®gheko, mbe i vonjimbughath…® vara na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Ňčgoreiye, vambe wein…®va Jisas rara Nasaret.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 68 Ko iyemaeŇčge Pita i roro iŇča, ‚ÄúMa ya ghareghare na ma nuwaŇčgu i rumwaruŇča budakai utuniya u utuutuna.‚ÄĚ Amba i wa iyena ve raŇčgi e ghamba raŇčgiko. E mbaŇčaniye amba kamkam i kula.\fig Pita i roro iŇča, ‚ÄúMa ya ghareghare na ma nuwaŇčgu i rumwaruŇča budakai utuniya u utuutuna.‚ÄĚ|alt="Pita denieshe knows Jesus" src="IB04158bw.tif" size="col" copy="Faadil" ref="14:66-68"\fig*
\p 
\v 69 MbaŇča wevoma vambowo i vaidiva Ňčgora ghamba raŇčgima na i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® ndeghath…® gheko iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalake iyake Jisas gharaghambu regha.‚ÄĚ
\v 70 Ko iyemaeŇčge Pita vambowo i rorova iŇča ma i ghareghare.
\p MbaŇča ubotu e ghereiye ghar…®ghar…®ma va th…® ndeghath…®ma mbowo th…® dageweva, ‚ÄúEmunjoru ghen ghanjiu regha ghen, kaiwae rara Galiliya ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 71 Pita i tholomundu na iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru Loi e marae ma ya ghareghare iya lolona hu utuuta utuniyena. ThoŇčgo ma ya utuŇča emunjoru Loi i lith…® e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 72 E mbaŇčako iyako kamkam i kula mbaŇčaiwoniye, na Pita i renuwaŇčakiki ŇčgoroŇčga Jisas meŇčamawe, ‚ÄúAmba muyai kamkam i kula mbaŇčaiwoniye, mbaŇčato ne uŇča ma u ghareghareŇčgo.‚ÄĚ Amba Pita gham…®nae i ghenenja moli na i randa lagh…®ye.
\c 15
\s1 Jisas i kot weya Pailat
\r (Mat 27:1-2,11-14; Luk 23:1-5; Jon 18:28-38)
\p 
\v 1 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye weinjiyaŇčgiya Jiu ghanjigiyagiya, mbaro gharavavaghare na ghanjiune vavanava Jiu e lenji kot lagh…®ye th…® woraweya lenji mbaro. Th…® Ňčgara Jisas th…® yovaŇčgu weya Pailat.
\v 2 Pailat i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Jiu lenji kiŇč?‚ÄĚ
\p Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiya iya moŇčana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® wonjoweya Jisas va i vakathaŇčgiya bigibigi raraithar…® i ghanagha.
\v 4 Pailat vambowo i vaitova iŇča, ‚ÄúMane u thombe? Wo u thuwe, th…® wonjoweŇčge e vakatha raraithar…® i ghanagha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas ma i ndegonjogha mun i vakatha Pailat ghare i yo.
\s1 Jisas o Barabas
\r (Mat 27:15-26; Luk 23:13-25; Jon 18:39‚Äď19:16)
\p 
\v 6 Theghathagha regha na regha Thaga ValaŇčani e t…®ne Pailat i vaŇčguvaŇčguraŇčgiya rayakuyaku e thiyo regha iya Jiu th…® tuthigiyawe.
\v 7 E mbaŇčako iyako amala regha idae Barabas ina e thiyo t…®ne weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavanava. Va th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgiya Rom gharambarombaro na th…® un…®gha lolo regha.
\v 8 MbaŇča wabwi lagh…®ye th…® mevathavatha, kaero th…® naŇčgo weya Pailat i vakatha weŇčgi Ňčgoreiya i vakavakatha theghathegha regha na regha e mbaŇčako iyako.
\v 9 Pailat i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwamiya ya rakayathu Jiu lenji kiŇč kaiwami?‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Pailat i ghareghare wagiyawe ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® yamwakabu na gharenji i gaith…®wana Jisas kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ko taulagh…® nuwanjiya iya kaiwae th…® vaŇčgugiyawe.
\p 
\v 11 Ko ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® vokumukumuŇčgiya wabwiko lagh…®ye na th…® dage weya Pailat na i rakayathu eŇčge Barabas.
\v 12 Pailat mbowo i vaitoŇčgiva wabwiko iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vakatha budakai weya reghake iya huŇčake Jiu lenji kiŇč?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Th…® kula njoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU rokros!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Ko Pailat i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae vara na ne ya vakatha iyako? Va i vakatha the thar…®?‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® kula na ghal…®Ňčanji ma i lagh…®ye eŇčge, ‚ÄúU rokros!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Kaiwae Pailat nuwaiya i vakathaŇčgi na th…® warari, i vakatha Barabas na i raŇčgi e thiyo kaiwanji, amba i vakatha Jisas na th…® yab…®b…® na i vaŇčgugiya weŇčgiya ragagaith…® na th…® Ňčge e kros.
\s1 Ragagaith…® th…® vakatha Jisas Ňčgoreiye // kiŇč na th…® vatabweyaruŇča
\r (Mat 26:67-68; 27:27-31; Luk 22:63-65; Jon 19:2-3)
\p 
\v 16 Ragagaith…® th…® yovaŇčguya Jisas gawana ele Ňčgolo ghayayao na th…® kula vathavathaŇčgiya ghanjiuneko wolagh…®ye th…® megh…®liŇča Jisas.
\v 17 Th…® liya kwama molao sosoro na th…® vanjimbowe, na th…® vona umbwa ele kinkin yaŇčgae na th…® th…®n…®rawe e umbaliye.
\v 18 Amba th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya yavwatata ghavakavakathawe na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúO Jiu lenji KiŇč, len mbaro ne i meghabana!‚ÄĚ
\v 19 Th…® wo umbwa na th…® ŇčgeŇčgeŇča umbaliye, th…® njoŇčgovun…®vun na th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye th…® kururu.
\v 20 MbaŇča th…® vatabweruŇčako na e ghereiye, th…® liraŇčgiya kwamako sosoro na th…® vanjimbo mbe amalagh…®niye ghakwamako. Amba th…® vaŇčguraŇčgiya na th…® yovaŇčgu veth…® rokros.
\s1 Th…® rokros Jisas
\r (Mat 27:32-44; Luk 23:26-43; Jon 19:17-27)
\p 
\v 21 E kamwath…® mborowa th…® lavolevola amala regha idae Saimon, rara Sairin, va i mena eto na ma i ruma e ghembako t…®ne. Ragagaith…®ko th…® vavur…®ghegheŇča na i wo Jisas ghakros. Amalagh…®niye le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Aleksanda na Rupas.
\p 
\v 22 Th…® yovaŇčguya Jisas e bobokulu idae Golgota (gharumwaru Boutouto Ghambae).
\v 23 Th…® th…®n…®giya weya waen va th…® liŇčgirawe weiye mbwa regha idae mer,\f + \fr 15:23 \ft Mer iye umbwa regha thiye, ne val…®kaiwae i vakatha v…®r…®ko seiwo i nja e kros…®ko vwatae.\f* ko mava i mun.
\v 24 MbaŇča th…® Ňčge e kros…®ko vwatae, amba th…® wobwiya ghakwamakwama. Th…® mbana var…®var…® na th…® mwadiwoŇča mwadiwo reghawe. Thela thoŇčgo i wo var…®ko iya e ghanonoko amba i tuthi iyaŇčganiya i bigi.
\p 
\v 25 MbaŇčambaŇča, varae vama naen klok th…® Ňčge Jisas e kros vwatae.
\v 26 Ghawonjowe r…®ghethoru va th…® rori na th…® Ňčge umbaliye ina yavoro iŇča, \sc Jiu Lenji KiŇč\sc*.
\v 27 Vambe th…® rokrosiŇčgiva rakaiv…® theghewo. Regha e une na regha e moiye.\f + \fr 15:27 \ft R…®ghethoruke iyake (15:28) ma ina Buk Boboma Togha tomethi lemoyo noroke. IŇčake: \fv 28 \ft Va Ňčgoreiyako na i vaemunjoruŇča ŇčgoroŇčga Buk Boboma le utu iŇča, ‚ÄúTh…® govatabo weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…®.‚ÄĚ\f*
\p 
\v 29 Ghar…®ghar…® th…® rakarakareŇča evasiwae th…® wovanukunukuya umbalinji na th…® goviyaviya ghamwae, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAe, va uŇča ne u tagarakaraka Ňägolo Boboma na mbaŇča thegheto e t…®ne kaero u vatad…®va.
\v 30 Tembe u vamora ghan…®mberegha. U roiteta kros…®na u njama!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare tembe th…® goviyaviyava ghamwae th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVa i vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana, ko ma val…®kaiwae i vamoru ghamberegha!
\v 32 Wo ra thuweno Mesaiya, Isirel lenji kiŇč, i njama e kros…®ko ko ambane ra thuwe na wo loŇčweghath…®.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i mare
\r (Mat 27:45-56; Luk 23:44-49; Jon 19:28-30)
\p 
\v 33 Ghararagh…®ye mboro vanautumako lagh…®ye i mouwo. Na i wo ghaghad t…®ri klok.
\v 34 Vama t…®ri klok amba Jisas i kula na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúEloi, Eloi, lama sabak…®tani,‚ÄĚ gharumwaru Ňčgoreiye, ‚ÄúLo Loi, lo Loi, buda kaiwae u iteteŇčaŇčgo?‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 15:34 \xt Sam 22:1\x*
\p 
\v 35 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana va thiya ndeghath…® gheko th…® loŇčwethavwiya ghal…®Ňčae na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo hu vandeŇče, i kula weya Ilaija iyako.‚ÄĚ
\v 36 Regha i yoruku weiye vune, i liutu e waen monyomonyo, i lirawe e umbwa mbothiye na i livoreŇča Jisas e ghae, na iŇča, ‚ÄúWo ra roroghagha na ra thuwe thare Ilaija ne i mena na i wonjoŇča e kros…®ko!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 37 Amba Jisas i randa na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye moli, na i liya yawaliye.
\p 
\v 38 MbaŇčako iyako kwama va i ganatena woluwolu bobomako moli e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne i mathethe wa yavoro na ve wo bode.
\p 
\v 39 Ragagaith…® lenji randeviva i ndeghath…® e ghamwae, i thuweya Jisas le mareko na iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjoru iye Loi Nariye!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 40 Elaela vavana va inanji gheko. Vambe th…® ndeghath…® bwagabwaga na th…® njimbukikiya Jisas. Inanji e t…®nenji Meri t…®nan Magadala, le ghaida Meri Jemes vamba iyovole eŇčge na Joses t…®nanji na Salome.
\v 41 Wanakauke thiyake va th…® ghambugha Jisas mbaŇča ina Galili na th…® thalavu e ghan…®Ňčga na bigibigi vavanava. Wanakau vavanava va th…® rakawe weinji Jerusalem vambe inanjiva gheko.
\s1 Josep rara Ar…®mathiya i beku Jisas
\r (Mat 27:57-61; Luk 23:50-56; Jon 19:38-42)
\p 
\v 42 Vama yegh…®yegh…®ye na kaiwae mbaŇča ghamba vivatha Sabat kaiwae,
\v 43 Josep rara Ar…®mathiya, iye Jiu lenji kot lagh…®ye loloniye regha. Ghayavwatata i lagh…®ye na vambe i roroghaghava Loi ghambaŇča mbaro kaiwae. Ghare i matuwo i wa weya Pailat na ve naŇčgo weya Jisas riwaekowe.
\v 44 Pailat ghare i yo mbaŇča i loŇčweya iyako. I kula weya ragagaith…® lenji randeviva na i vaito thoŇčgo Jisas mbe kaero me mare.
\v 45 MbaŇča i loŇčweya ragagaith…®ko lenji randevivako le utu iŇča Jisas kaero me mare, Pailat i vatomweya riwaeko weya Josep.
\v 46 Josep i vamoda kwama kakaleva yaŇčgara modae lagh…®ye, i wonjoŇča Jisas riwaeko na i ghavowe. I wo na ve worawe ele ghabubu va th…® t…®gh…® e var…® regha Ňčgora maŇčgavar…®ma. Amba i vabulale var…® lagh…®ye regha na i wogana ghaekowe.
\v 47 Meri t…®nan Magadala na Meri Joses t…®nae th…® njimbukiki na th…® thuwe wagiyawe aŇčga meth…® woraweya Jisas riwae.
\c 16
\s1 Jisas i thuweiru na e yawayawaliye
\r (Mat 28:1-8; Luk 24:1-12; Jon 20:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Jiu lenji Sabat iko na e ghereiye Meri t…®nan Magadala, Meri Jemes t…®nae na Salome va th…® vamoda bunama butiye lagh…®ye na i thovuye. Nuwanjiya th…® wa na veth…® varuvo Jisas riwaemawe.
\v 2 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča e Sande, varae vama i yovoro amba th…® wa e ghabubuko.
\v 3 E kamwath…® mborowa th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThela ne i vabulale var…®ma e ghabubuko ghae kaiwanda?‚ÄĚ
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča th…® vutha th…® tagath…®na maranji na th…® thuwe var…®ko kaiwae lagh…®ye moli, kaero meth…® vabulale vakatha.
\v 5 MbaŇča th…® rakaru e ghabubuko t…®ne, veth…® vaidiya amala regha tabwagha, i yaku e val…®vaŇčga une na i njimbo kwama molao kakaleva. Gharenji i tagath…®n lagh…®ye moli.
\p 
\v 6 I dage weŇčgi, ‚ÄúGharemi tha i tage. Ya ghareghare hu tamwe Jisas rara Nasaret, iye amba mendake th…® rokros. Kaero me thuweiru na ma ina gheke. Wo hu thuwe ghambaeke mendava th…® worakewe!
\v 7 Ko hu njogha na vohu dage weŇčgiya gharaghambuma na Pita mbe Ňčgoreiyeva. HuŇča ‚ÄėKaero i viva e ghamwami Galili. Ne vohu vaidi gheko, Ňčgorava le utuutuma weŇčga.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® voiteta ghabubuko weinji lenji mararu na lenji gharelagh…®lagh…® lagh…®ye. Ma veth…® ndeutu mun weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® kaiwae thiya mararu.
\s1 Jisas i yomara weya Meri t…®nan Magadala
\p 
\v 9 Sande mbaŇčambaŇča moli, Jisas le thuweiru e mare e ghereiye, i yomarakai weya Meri t…®nan Magadala, iyava i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyaoma raraithar…® theghepir…®mawe.
\v 10 I wa weŇčgiya Jisas gharaghambuko iyava weiyaŇčgiko na ve utugiya weŇčgi. Vambe inanjiwe nuwanji i thar…® na thiya randa.
\v 11 Ko mbaŇča th…® loŇčwe Meri iŇča, ‚ÄúJisas kaero me thuweiru na ma thuwe e maraŇčgu,‚ÄĚ ma th…® loŇčweghath…®.
\s1 Jisas i yomara weŇčgiya gharaghambu theghewo
\r (Luk 24:13-35)
\p 
\v 12 Iyake e ghereiye, Jisas i yomara weŇčgiya gharaghambu theghewo na ghayamoyamo vambe regha, mbaŇča va mbema veth…® loŇčga eŇčge eto.
\v 13 MbaŇča th…® ghareghare amalagh…®niye amba th…® njogha na veth…® utugiya weŇčgiya gharaghambuko, ko iyemaeŇčge mava th…® loŇčweghath…®.
\s1 Jisas i yomara weŇčgiya gharaghambu theyaworo na regha
\r (Mat 28:16-20; Luk 24:36-49; Jon 20:11-23; Vak 1:6-8)
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča reghava i yomara weŇčgiya gharaghambu theyaworo na regha, mbaŇčaniye vara thiya ghan…®Ňčga. Jisas i Ňčaebaruru wanaŇčgi kaiwae mava th…® loŇčweghath…® na mbe Ňčgoreiyeva gharenji le vur…®gheghe kaiwae, kaiwae mava th…® loŇčweghath…®Ňčgiya thavala va th…® thuwe le thuweiru e ghereiye.
\v 15 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu rakaraŇčgi e yambaneke lagh…®ye na vohu vavaghareŇča Toto Thovuye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye.
\v 16 Thela ne i loŇčweghath…® na i bap…®taiso Loi ne i vamora yawaliye, ko thela ma i loŇčweghath…® Loi ne i giya vuyowo weya loloko iyako.
\v 17 Thavala ne th…® loŇčweghath…®, Loi ne i giya vur…®gheghe weŇčgi na th…® vakathaŇčgiya vakatha ghamba rotaele i ghanagha. E idaŇčgu ne th…® variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, ne th…® utu e ghal…®ghal…®Ňča totogha vavanava.
\v 18 ThoŇčgo ne th…® yalaweŇčgiya mwatamwata raraithar…® o th…® muna mamate, mane i th…®vathar…®Ňčgi. Ne th…® bigiraweya n…®man…®manji ghambweghambwera e riwanji na riwanji i thovuye.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jisas i voro e buruburu
\r (Luk 24:50-53; Vak 1:9-11)
\p 
\v 19 MbaŇča Giya Jisas i utuvao weŇčgi amba Loi i vakatha na i voro e buruburu na i yaku Loi e une e ghamba yavwatata.
\v 20 Gharaghambu th…® rakaraŇčgi na veth…® vavaghareŇča Toto Thovuye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye. Giya Jisas i thalavuŇčgi na i vakatha lenji vavaghare emunjoru weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® kaiwae va th…® thuwe vakathaŇčgiko ghamba rotaele th…® vakathako e maranji. 
